\id MRK MARKUS - Hona Bible
\h Markus
\toc3 Markus
\toc2 Markus
\toc1 Markus
\mt1 Markus
\c 1
\s1 Tangsang Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisma kwamanaɗǝ
\r (Matta3:1-12; Luka3:1-9,15-17; Yahaya1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Katǝra ɗeleewar tǝ Peɗǝnda aten Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti, Wan Faara.
\v 2 Chirethleng nda hai hu ɗeleewar annabi Ishaya tǝ ndaarha,
\q1 “Niya ˈwa thlǝn tǝ thlǝndǝna ɗǝ ma sa,
\q2 na a takso kwamana ɗǝ” \x * \xo 1:2 \xt Malachi3:1\x*
\q1 
\v 3 “Urarha a aah farha a kaheerha.
\q1 ‘Taksaman kwamana Chinǝm sǝ
\q2 pǝpǝnaman kwaman sarya ɗǝ a ndǝghǝn.’” \x * \xo 1:3 \xt Ishaya40:3\x*
\b
\p 
\v 4 Yahaya kyagha ɓa a kahedɗi nagha a ndang nda fiya a malangganda ɗimiyid ndan fananggǝn kanda yi chakh ɗimiyirha.
\v 5 Kahad fiya na a chehweed Yahuda tǝ fiya heu na a Urshalima kyanda ɓa ɗǝnda thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ. Malang nda ɗimiyid ndan ǝnangga Yahaya mbaptisǝma kanda a kufad Urdun.
\p 
\v 6 Yahaya kalɗǝ lukrha ǝnana nda tǝ was thlǝkhmu, ƙǝnanggǝn muwun tǝ paama, mbeeya tǝ ɗee ndǝna ǝnnadghǝn mii.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft 2 Kutǝrya 1:8\f*
\v 7 Ndanggǝn fiya, “Na niifa sǝ ɓayi a samadna na tǝ sǝsǝmnda fa kalgha nggi mu, sahad pahamggǝn tsǝkki na a kwasang nggi hai wa.
\v 8 Ənanggi mbaptisǝma kun tǝ aama, amma ndǝghǝnggi nǝn a ǝnang mbaptisǝma kun tǝ sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda.”
\s1 Ənang nda mbaptisǝma Yeeso
\r (Matta3:13-17; Luka3:21-22)
\p 
\v 9 A hu sayidɗi kee ɓagha Yeeso ɓa a Nadzarat na hu chehweed Nggalili ǝnangga Yahaya mbaptisǝma a kufad Urdun.
\v 10 Nana Yeeso a kyarha sǝ hu aamɗi kee, ƙǝlagha hai talara inɗaɗǝ nagha Sǝsǝn Faara a tǝraa tenggǝn hai ƙǝla tǝtiliurha.
\v 11 Sǝk urarha nda a talara hai, “Sani Waana, nggǝmni niyi a tǝk mbǝnduwa fa kaan.”\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Katǝrarha 22:2; Dzabura 2:7; Ishaya 42:1; Matta 3:17; 12:8; Markus 9:7; Luka 3:22\f*
\s1 Ƙǝƙǝrang Sheetan Yeeso
\r (Matta4:1-11; Luka4:1-13)
\p 
\v 12 Tsu kee tǝrangga Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda a kaheerha ɗǝ,
\v 13 tsauka a kahedɗi yi ɓeena kumggit faɗa nagha sheetan a ƙǝƙǝrang nda. Ndǝghǝn a kahedɗi tǝ thlukkya yi heerha, nagha fathlǝngya Faara a ǝnang taara.
\s1 Katǝrang Yeeso targhǝn hai
\r (Matta4:12-17; Luka4:14-15)
\p 
\v 14 A kwasamadɗi muwang nanda Yahaya ahu porsǝna ɗǝ, ɗǝgha Yeeso Nggalili ɗǝ nagha a pǝr laɓar Faara.
\v 15 Nagha a ndaarha, “Ɓad sayidɗa ɓa, kutǝryid Faara nduwusɗa ɓa. Malaman ɗimiyid nun fǝrƙǝkafek nun tǝ Laɓarɗi na Mbǝnggǝn.”\f + \fr 1:15 \ft Matta 3:2\f*
\p 
\v 16 Nduwusna Yeeso mii kufad Nggalili ɗǝ, na Siman nǝn tǝ wan man Andrawus a muk panggama a kufadɗi ƙǝsǝr kanda fa ƙǝs tǝngya ni.
\v 17 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Ɓama ɓa, mbuwama samadna, niya tsawang kun fa ƙǝs fiya ɓa.”
\v 18 Tsu a mbǝɗi kee malangganda panggamggi ndan mbu samadghǝn nda.
\p 
\v 19 Ɗǝnǝn mbeeɗǝ, na Yakubu nǝn tǝ wanman Yahaya wangya Dzabaɗi ahu kwambuwol, kanda a tangsang panggamnggi ndan ɗǝ.
\v 20 Nana Yeeso kanda aah kanda nǝn, mal chi ndan nda Dzabaɗi ahu kwambuwol ɗi tǝ fingya nafiya na a ɗang kanda sǝ mbu samadghǝn nda.
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso niifa na tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa
\r (Luka4:31-37)
\p 
\v 21 Ɗǝnda Kafarnahum ɗǝ, nduwusna far yiɓǝd Yahudaya ɓa, kyagha Yeeso Ƙǝn Faara ɗǝ katǝranggǝn tsaharhaha.
\v 22 Nagha fiya ǝnwulteena a ten tsahadghǝn ha, ƙǝsǝr tsahanggǝn kanda ha ƙǝla niifa na tǝ ngyakhrha ha, mbǝ ƙǝla fa malǝmngya yi ɗeleewar Musa wa. \x * \xo 1:22 \xt Matta7:28-29\x*
\p 
\v 23 Tǝrgha ahu ƙǝn hwan Faarɗan na niifa sǝ na tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa huhwaagha,
\v 24 ndǝghǝn, “Mana midwa tǝ kan, Yeeso tǝ Nadzarat? Ɓana ɓa ka ɓǝlangga kan wa? Sǝnɗi sa, na chahal yi Faara!”
\v 25 Yanangga Yeeso, “Nggǝlang miiwa! Kyosǝ a fadghǝn.”
\p 
\v 26 Muwangga ǝnkaheedɗi hweeɗe hai, huhwaagha, kyagha sǝ a fadghǝn.
\p 
\v 27 Fiya na a mbǝɗi ka ǝnwulteena na nda a ndang nda ndan, “Tur maniya? Weerinda tsaharhaha tǝ ngyakhrha! Nǝn yanang ǝnkaheeya na nda a takkwa miighǝn.”
\p 
\v 28 Laɓarghǝn welɗaɗǝ ƙǝkar ahu chehweed Nggalili.
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso Fiya hangga
\r (Matta8:14-15; Luka4:38-39)
\p 
\v 29 Kyana nda hai ahu Ƙǝn Faara, nda Yakubu tǝ Yahaya ɗǝnda wuri ki Mbiturus ɗǝ tǝ Andrawus.
\v 30 Thlaɓǝr Mbiturus tǝnuwunda fadghǝn ɓee kalth hu sǝra, pǝrang nggǝnda Yeeso.
\v 31 Ɗǝgha Yeeso thlǝmad nuɗaɗǝ, ƙǝs harghǝnǝn thlenggǝn sǝ.
\v 32 A figrha mukna yanfaara hai ɓagha fiya thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa tǝ nafiya na fandan ɓee tǝ fingya na tǝ ǝnkaheeya fa.
\v 33 Nafiya na ahu talɗi wuma nda kwatkirǝm ɗa ɓa.
\v 34 Ƙǝnangga Yeeso fiya hangga na tǝ wanhaaya fa ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn. Kyanggǝn ǝnkaheeya sǝ hangga na a fad fiya, amma mbǝ malang ǝnkaheeyini kala nda sǝ wa ƙǝsǝr sǝn ndan.
\s1 Hwan Yeeso Faara a mbǝrha na ɓǝɓee
\r (Luka4:42-44)
\p 
\v 35 A tsar ƙǝrǝt, ka pit mbǝrha ɓa, thliigha Yeeso sǝ ɗǝgha mbǝrha ɗǝ na ɓǝɓee hwan Faara nǝn.
\v 36 Mbiturus tǝ ka wiyighǝn ɗǝnda ka kaɗadghǝn ɗǝ,
\v 37 walang nanda, ndang ngganda, “Fiya kahad a kaɗa sa!”
\p 
\v 38 Nggǝmangga Yeeso kanda, “Taama mbǝrha ɗǝ pak ahu talya ɗǝ na tsau tǝni ɗǝ pǝr laɓarɗi a mbǝɗi ƙǝm. Ndǝghǝnni ɓani ɓa ka manggǝn.”
\p 
\v 39 Wenggǝn chehweed Nggalili hai nagha a pǝr laɓar Faara ahu ƙǝn tsahad Yahudaya tǝ kyang nda ǝnkaheeya sǝ.
\s1 Niifa na tǝ wanhad termeerha
\r (Matta8:1-4; Luka5:12-16)
\p 
\v 40 Niifa na tǝ wanhad termeerha fa ɓagha thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ɓǝrgha hai tǝ waɗedghǝn hwanggǝnǝn, ndanggǝn, “A nggǝmna fa, tsaɓee ɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 41 Haɗangga niifɗi Yeeso fa, tǝrangga Yeeso harghǝn sǝ tsuwarghǝnǝn fa ndanggǝn, “Nggǝmɗifa, tsaɓuɗǝ.”
\v 42 Tsu a mbǝɗi kee, kyagha termedɗa sǝ a fadghǝn ƙǝngga.
\p 
\v 43 Ƙǝsgha Yeeso thlǝmadghǝn, ndanggǝn,
\v 44 “A pǝrang nan niifa wa. Amma ɗuwaɗǝ, a kyaɗang fadwa firis ǝna sataka na ƙǝla ndana ngyakhrha ɗeleewar Musa a kyaɗang ndaarha nǝn kanda tsabna ɗǝ.” \x * \xo 1:44 \xt Livitikus14:1-32\x*
\p 
\v 45 A meghedghǝn kyagha niifɗa hai nagha a pǝrghǝn. Ndǝn ǝnagha ndǝn, ɓalwa Yeeso nggǝr kyarha hur tala hai a pǝpal amma ishgha a ƙǝsǝr wure a mbǝrha mbuwana niifa sǝ. Ko nanǝn kee na fiya naarha ɓarha thlǝmadghǝn ɓa a mbǝya ɓa hangga.
\c 2
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso niifa mǝrna fadghǝn hai
\r (Matta9:1,8; Luka5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Mǝngwaha wa, nggǝrgha Yeeso kyarha Kafarnahum hai, sǝkka fiya ndaarha ɓaɗǝ wure ɓa.
\v 2 Wumngga fiyaɓa, lǝɗang ngganda ƙǝnɗi ta mii kwatminda ɓa, a nagha a pǝrang laɓar Faara kanda.
\v 3 Ɓagha nafiya ɓa faɗa tǝ niifa mǝrna fadghǝn hai.
\v 4 Walwa nda kwamana wa ƙǝsǝr ka hangnda fiya. Thlǝɓangganda ten ƙǝnɗa ɗǝ mǝmǝl tǝ man ten Yeeso fǝrghǝn nda hai tǝ ɗǝngǝlɗi hunangganda hai a mbed Yeeso.
\p 
\v 5 Nana Yeeso fǝrƙǝkafǝkkin ndan, ndanggǝn hadɗi na kath, “Waana chohonda ɗimiyidwa ɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 6 Nanǝn ya, fasǝngya ngyakhrha tǝ Farisaya kanda a numarha tǝ ndaarha,
\v 7 “Kama na niifɗi ndaarha kee ya? Tǝ sar farha ni! Mbǝ niifa sǝ na chakh ɗimiyirha wa ƙǝl Faara katenggǝn.”
\p 
\v 8 Tsu kee sǝngga Yeeso ǝnɗi nanda a numarha ahur ndan, ndanggǝn kanda, “Kama nun a numarha aten ǝngginiya?
\v 9 Yanggini pǝpa, ndanggǝm tǝ mǝrra fadɗa hai, ‘Chohonda ɗimiyidwa ɗǝ wa,’ nduwa ndam, ‘Thliusǝ, tǝrang ɗǝnggǝl wa wiu wa?’
\v 10 Amma a sǝnunsǝ Wan niifa nǝghǝn tǝ sǝsǝmnda ha hu ƙǝshidɗiya yi chakh ɗimiya.” Ndanggǝn niifɗi mǝrna fadghǝn hai,
\p 
\v 11 “Ndoyi, thliusǝ tǝrang ɗǝggǝl wa wiina wureɗǝ.”
\v 12 Thliigha sǝ tǝranggǝn ɗǝnggǝlghǝn kyagha hai a yid fiya heu. Ənɗiya fǝrang ɗǝ ǝnwulteena kanda na nda a fal Faara, na nda a ndaarha, “ˈWawum na tur ǝnɗiya wa.”
\s1 Yeeso aahɗǝ Lawi
\r (Matta9:9-13; Luka5:27-32)
\p 
\v 13 Nggǝrgha Yeeso ɗǝrha mii kufad Nggalili ɗǝ. Ɓagha fiya hangga thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, nagha a tsahang kanda ha.
\v 14 Nanǝn a mbǝra ɗǝ, na Lawi nǝn wan Halfa tsau a thlǝ tsamnda. Ndanggǝn, “Mbuwu samadna.” Thliigha Lawi sǝ mbu samadghǝnǝn.
\p 
\v 15 Nana Yeeso a hǝb ǝnnarhami a minda ki Lawi, fa thlǝ tsamngya hangga tǝ fa “ɗimiya” na nda a hǝbrha tǝghǝn tǝ fatsahayighǝn, ƙǝsǝr fiya hangga mbuwa samadghǝn.
\v 16 Nana fa sǝngya ɗeleewar Musa na Farisaya na nandan a hǝbrha tǝ fa “Ɗimiya” tǝ fa thlǝ tsamngya, tsahang mee nda fatsahayighǝn, “Kama nǝn a hǝbrha tǝ fa thlǝ tsamngya tǝ fa ‘Ɗimiya’?”
\p 
\v 17 Sǝkna Yeeso kee ndanggǝn kanda, “Mbǝ nafiya na ƙǝkanglang kaɗa tǝ purha wa, Ƙǝl haaya. Ɓawi ka aah nafiya ɓa na a ǝna nggayirha wa, amma fa ɗimiya.”
\s1 Tsakhmee aten kar aama
\r (Matta9:14-17; Luka5:33-39)
\p 
\v 18 Fatsahaya Yahaya tǝ Farisaya na nda kar aama. Ɓagha fingya thlǝmadghǝn ɓa tsahang mee nda Yeeso, “Mani ǝnagha ndǝn, fatsahaya Yahaya tǝ yi Farisaya kanda a kar aama, amma finayiwa mba nda ǝnaarha wa?”
\p 
\v 19 Nggǝmangga Yeeso kanda, “Pashiya wutsamnda na nda kar aama wutsamnda ɓalɗǝ a thlǝmad ndan wa? A ɓal wutsamnda a thlǝman ndan mba nda ǝnaarha wa.
\v 20 Na sayi ɓayi ɓana nda tǝrang wutsamndǝɗi ma kanda. A mbǝɗaniya ɓa nanda kar aama.
\p 
\v 21 “Mbǝ niifa sǝ na njar ɓar kaɓarha ɓa mbuhanggǝnǝn suhurra lukrha fa wa. A ǝna ɗǝ kee, mbuhudɗi na tǝ kukwasharra ɓar kaɓadɗi nǝn njaara hai a fad luwudɗi kal yanɗa nǝn mu na kaar.
\v 22 Mbǝ niifa sǝ na irang weerǝnda aam inabi ahu suhurra samsami hai wa. A ǝna ɗǝ kee, na weerǝnda aam inabi ɗi ɗathlang nda samsami ɗa ɗǝ. Nǝn iraɗǝ, sǝbgha samsami ɗa ɗǝ. Kamɗǝ weerǝnda aam inabi nǝm irangnda ahur weerǝnda samsami hai.”
\s1 Tsakhmee aten far yibrha
\r (Matta12:1-8; Luka6:1-5)
\p 
\v 23 Na farɗa sǝ, far Yibrha Yahudaya, Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn tǝrnda kwaman heerha; tǝrgha fatsahayighǝn kya ten ǝnnarhami nda na ƙǝla wan hwaliirha fahwang ngganda hai na nda a kiighǝn.\f + \fr 2:23 \ft Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 23:25\f*
\v 24 Ndagha Farisaya, “Mani na fatsahayiwa ǝna ˈya kee, ˈyaɗana ngyakhrha Musa yi far Yibrha?”
\p 
\v 25 Nggǝmangga Yeeso kanda, “Karatang ngwanun ǝnɗi na hu ɗeleewar Faara ǝnana Ndauda tǝ nafighǝn na miirha a ƙǝs kanda wa?
\v 26 A thlakh mbǝd Abiyata mamnda firis, kyanǝn hu Ƙǝn Faara ɗǝ tǝrnǝn mburodi sǝ ɗǝfangna nda ɗǝ ka firis katenggǝn, kiigha ǝnangǝn pashiya wiyighǝn ha.”\x * \xo 2:26 \xt Livitikus24:9\x*\f + \fr 2:26 \ft Firistaya 24:9\f*
\v 27 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Əna nanda far yibrha ka niifa, mbǝ niifa ka far yibrha wa.
\v 28 Nanǝn kee, Wan Niifa Chinǝm ni heu tǝ far Yibrha.”
\c 3
\s1 Niifa mǝrna harghǝn hai a Kafarnahum
\r (Matta12:9-14; Luka6:6-11)
\p 
\v 1 Na farɗa sǝ fadɗǝn, kyagha Yeeso Ƙǝn Faara ɗǝ, na niifa sǝ mǝrna harghǝn hai ahur ƙǝnɗi.
\v 2 Na nafiya sǝ na mindan a ƙǝsangganda Yeeso tǝ ɗimiyirha, ƙǝlaghǝn nda ha tǝnǝn a ƙǝnang nda niifɗi a far yibrha.
\p 
\v 3 Ndangga Yeeso niifɗi mǝrna harghǝn hai, “Thliusǝ ɓa isha a mbed fiya.”
\v 4 Tǝrgha tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Yanggini mǝmǝl a ǝnam a far Yibrha? Əna nggayirha nǝm wa nduwa mbǝlfeerha wa, a hǝrghanggǝm yibrha wa nduwa ɓǝlanggǝm wa?”
\p 
\v 5 Ƙǝlangga Yeeso kanda tǝ sǝbrha hura tǝ ƙǝm ǝn kawani ka kakrakkid ten ndan. Ndanggǝn niifɗi, “Pǝpǝnang harwa ɗǝ.” Pǝpǝnanggǝn harghǝn ɗǝ, a mbǝɗi kee nggǝrgha harghǝn ɓa ƙǝla kaar.
\v 6 Tǝrgha Farisayini kya nda ƙǝshaaɗǝ ɗa nda ndikrha tǝ nafiya Hirdus na a kaɗa kwaman ɓǝllang nda Yeeso.
\s1 Mbu fiya samad Yeeso
\p 
\v 7 Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn ɗǝnda mii kufad Nggalili ɗǝ, fiya hangga mbuwa samadghǝn.
\v 8 Hǝrǝm nanda sǝk ǝngya ǝnanǝn heu, fiya hangga ɓagha ɓa a Yahuda, tǝ Urshalima, tǝ Idomiya, tǝ fingya na a pǝm kufad Urdun, tǝ nafiya Taya tǝ Sidon.
\v 9 Ka hangnda fiya ndangga Yeeso fa tsahayighǝn a ɓang kombuwol nda ɓa na ngguchit amana fiya ˈyaɓang mbǝrha fa.
\v 10 Ƙǝsǝr ˈwaɗǝ teena ƙǝnang ɗǝ fiya hangga, ndǝn ǝnagha ndǝn fingya na tǝ wanhaaya fa kanda a ˈwaarha mbee ɓa ka a tsǝwarghǝn nda fa. \x * \xo 3:10 \xt Markus4:1; Luka5:1-3\x*
\v 11 Kala sayidɗi nana sǝsǝn mbǝlfeeya ndǝn, ƙǝl na nda fǝla hai a mbedghǝn na nda a ndaarha, “Wan Faara ni Sa.”
\p 
\v 12 Amma ƙǝsɗǝ thlǝman ndan a pǝr ndan tǝ wunni ndǝghǝn wa.
\s1 Wur Yeeso fa thlǝnggighǝn kumkap sǝri
\r (Matta10:1-4; Luka6:12-16)
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrgha Yeeso wumnda sǝ, aah fingyayina nǝn ɓa na midghǝn, ɗǝnda thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ.
\v 14 Wurgha hasǝ ahur ndan Kum kap sǝri, aah kanda nǝn fathlǝnggighǝn, a tsawa nda tǝghǝn tǝ ƙǝm a nagha thlǝn kanda ka pǝr laɓar Faara ɗǝ,
\v 15 tǝ wal ngyakhrha na kyangganda ǝnkaheeya sǝ.
\v 16 Kulo nafini kumkap sǝri wurnǝn ya.
\b
\li1 Siman, ɗǝfang na Yeeso thlǝma Mbiturus,
\li1 
\v 17 Yakubu wan Dzabadi tǝ wanman na Yahaya.
\li1 Ɗǝfangna Yeeso thlǝma kanda Mbuwadjis, ndaarha ni “Wangya Tǝrˈyana.”
\li1 
\v 18 Andrawus,
\li1 Filibus,
\li1 Mbatalomi,
\li1 Matta,
\li1 Toma,
\li1 Yakubu wan Halfa,
\li1 Tandawus,
\li1 Siman tǝ sǝrǝk chehweedghǝn.
\li1 
\v 19 Tǝ Yahuda Iskaryoti, fǝrgha Yeeso.
\s1 Yeeso tǝ Mbaˈaldzabul
\r (Matta12:22-32; Luka11:14-23; 12:10)
\p 
\v 20 Tǝrgha Yeeso kyagha ahur minda hai, nggǝrgha fiya wumnda ɓa, ndǝghǝn tǝ fa tsahayighǝn mba nda wal kwaman ǝna ˈya mii wa.
\v 21 Sǝkna hurfayighǝn ǝnɗi nǝn a ǝnaarha, ɗǝnda ɗǝ ka a ƙǝsangganda, ƙǝsǝr na fiya a ndaarha, “Kyahar hutenggǝn hai.”
\p 
\v 22 Fa malǝmngya ngyakhrha ɓagha ɓa Urshalima ndaa nda, “Nǝghǝn tǝ Mbaˈaldzabul fa! Tǝ ngyakhrha Mbaˈaldzabul ni nǝn a kyang ǝnkaheeya sǝ.” \x * \xo 3:22 \xt Matta9:34; 10:25\x*
\p 
\v 23 Aagha Yeeso kanda ɓa thlǝghang karapu nǝn kanda sǝ, “Na sheetan ƙǝn na mbang kyang Sheetan sǝ?”
\v 24 A tsakh kutǝryirha hai sǝri, mbǝ kutǝryidɗi isha wa.
\v 25 A tsakh wure hai sǝri, mbǝ wuriɗi isha wa.
\v 26 Ana Sheetan a yan altenggǝn tǝ ƙǝm tsakhka hai, mbǝ mbang isha wa. Ɓa ngwala ɓenggǝn ɓa.
\p 
\v 27 Ƙǝkafek, mbǝ niifa sǝ na kyarha minda ki niifa hai na kanglang wiigha tǝ ǝnggighǝn wa ƙǝl ma ˈwaɗǝ teena ƙǝnangɗǝ niifɗa hai na kanglang ˈwan. A mbanggǝn har karid wurighǝn.
\p 
\v 28 “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, ɗimiya na heu tǝ sarfaya ǝnana fiya na nda chahanggǝn kanda ɗǝ.
\v 29 Amma kala niifa sargha Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda mba tam chahanggǝn ɗǝ wa, ǝnaɗǝ ɗimiyirha yi pa kwanɗǝ.”\f + \fr 3:29 \ft Luka 12:10\f*
\p 
\v 30 Thlǝkna Yeeso ndǝn kee ƙǝsǝr na nda a ndaarha, “Nǝghǝn tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa.”
\s1 Man Yeeso tǝ Wanmanggighǝn
\r (Matta12:46-50; Luka8:19-21)
\p 
\v 31 Tǝrgha ɓagha man Yeeso ɓa tǝ wanmanggighǝn. Isha nda a ƙǝshi thlǝn farha nda ɗa nda aaghǝn ɓa.
\v 32 Fiya wumngga hai muwang nda maɗufu hai, ndang ngganda, “Muwa tǝ wanmanggiwa kanda a ƙǝshi kanda a kaɗa sa.”
\p 
\v 33 Tsakhmee nǝn, “Nda wunni iiya tǝ wanmanggina?”
\p 
\v 34 Tǝrgha ƙǝlanggǝn fiya muwangga maɗufu hai ndǝghǝn, “Kulo nda iiya ya tǝ wanmanggina!
\v 35 Kala niifa ǝnagha taara tǝ ˈya na mid Faara tsauɗǝ wan pa tǝ wan nya tǝ iiya.”
\c 4
\s1 Karapu aten tǝhǝfrha
\r (Matta13:1-9; Luka8:4-8)
\p 
\v 1 Yeeso nggǝrghǝn ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ tǝ tsahang fiya ha a mii wuri aam Nggalili. Fiya wumngga thlǝmadghǝn ɓa mulnda hai kaan pa kyagha hu kombuwol hai fiya tsǝtsau a mii ƙǝkǝshɓang nda.\f + \fr 4:1 \ft Luka 5:1-3\f*
\v 2 Tsahang ɗǝ ǝngya kanda ha hangga tǝ karapuya. A hu tsahadghǝn ha ndǝghǝn,
\v 3 “Kama thlǝmarha hai! Tǝ huɗarha ɗǝɗǝ ka hǝfrha ɗǝ.
\v 4 Nanǝn aten wash wiidɗi, hǝrgha fingya hai aten kwamana, ɓagha wuɗikkya ɓa ɗamangganda.
\v 5 Hǝrgha fingya hǝreng keela hai, ka mbuwana chehweerha sǝ ngga kya nda sǝ ƙǝkar, ƙǝsǝr mbǝ chehweedghǝn kuɗimnggǝn wa.
\v 6 Amma tǝkna yanfaara hai, hwara nda ɗǝ, ƙǝsǝr kwa wanda thlaara hai wa.
\v 7 Fingya hǝra nda pathlang ndakhkya hai kya nda sǝ kal wanda farha hai a pathlang ndakhkini wa ko kanda ǝna wee.
\v 8 Amma fingya hǝra nda hu chehweerha hai na ngga kyanda sǝ ǝna wee nda fingya katǝra kumnggit mahan-mahan, fingya ƙǝm kumnggit mikki-mikki har haru-haru.”
\v 9 Ndǝghǝn, “Yi na tǝ thlǝmad sǝkrha, sǝkƙǝnǝn.”
\p 
\v 10 Sayidɗi nanǝn katenggǝn, kumkap sǝri ɗi tǝ fingya na a thlǝmadghǝn tsahang mee nda ha aten karapu yini.
\v 11 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Nggǝmang nda kun fa na a sǝn ˈya nun na kutǝryid Faara ahurghǝn, fingya a mbǝ tǝ karapu wa mba nda sǝnggǝn wa.
\v 12 Tǝna nda,
\q1 “‘Ƙǝlaarha ɗǝ, amma mba nda kukwalang hai wa,
\q2 na nda sǝkƙǝn ƙǝm, amma mba nda sǝnang hai wa.
\q1 Kam kyahar nda ɓa,
\q2 chahang ɗimiyid ndan nda kanda ɗǝ!’ ”\x * \xo 4:12 \xt Ishaya6:9-10\x*
\s1 Pǝr Yeeso ten karapu ɗi
\r (Matta13:18-23; Luka8:11-15)
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Ashe sǝnanggun karapu ɗa hai ya wa, ƙǝƙǝn nun sǝn fingya karapuya?
\v 14 Tǝ hǝfǝdɗi, laɓar Faara ni nǝn a pǝra.
\v 15 Wiidɗi hǝrgha aten kwamana hai nǝghǝn aten nafiya sǝkka laɓarɗi, amma ɓagha Sheetan ɓa tǝranggǝn laɓar ɗaɗǝ ahur ndan.
\v 16 Fingya, na nda ƙǝla wiirha hǝf nanda a hǝreng keela, sǝk nanda laɓarɗi thlǝghǝn nda tǝ hura pǝpet.
\v 17 Amma mbuwana thlar ndan sǝ, mǝngwanda ha wa. A hǝrǝm ɓillarha nduwa sǝsaarha ɓarha ɓa ƙǝsǝr ka laɓarɗi mba nda kwas kyaharra hai wa.
\v 18 Tǝ ƙǝm na fingya ƙǝla wiiya hǝrgha pathlang ndakhkya hai, sǝkka laɓarɗi;
\v 19 amma ƙǝsǝr ɓillad ƙǝshiirha, tǝ suna ƙǝna tǝ nggǝm ǝn ƙǝshiirha thluranggǝn laɓarɗi ahur ndan tsauka mbǝ ˈyani na ngga wa.
\v 20 Wiiya hǝrgha hu chehweerha hai na ngga, nafiyani sǝkka laɓar Faara thlǝghǝnda fa tǝ chikrha katǝra kumnggit mahan-mahan, kumnggit mikki-mikki tǝ haru-haru aten ǝnɗi hǝf nanda.”
\s1 Patilla tsǝtsǝɓa tǝ tǝɓa
\r (Luka8:16-18)
\p 
\v 21 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “ˈWad niifa ɓarha ɓa tǝ patilla tsǝɓanggǝn tǝ tǝɓa nduwa ɗǝfanggǝn kasǝra ɗǝ wa? Mbǝ nǝm ɗǝfang nda a mbǝd ɗǝfǝdghǝn wa?\x * \xo 4:21 \xt Matta5:15; Luka11:33\x*
\v 22 Mbǝ ˈyasǝ na ɓǝɓee mbuwa kyarha sǝ wa. Mbǝ ˈyasǝ ƙǝm na nggǝnggǝla mbuwa wa kyarha pǝpal ɓa wa. \x * \xo 4:22 \xt Matta10:26; Luka12:2\x*
\v 23 Kala niifa na tǝ thlǝmad sǝkrha sǝkƙǝnǝn.”
\p 
\v 24 “Kwarama tǝ sǝk pathla nun naarha sǝkrha, tur tasau ƙǝƙǝrɗi nun a ƙǝƙǝrra sǝ, ndǝghǝnni na nda a ƙǝƙǝrang kunsǝ ƙǝm har kal yinun nǝn mu.” \x * \xo 4:24 \xt Matta7:2; Luka6:3\x*
\v 25 “Kala niifa na tǝ ˈya ha na nda a chighanggǝn, kala niifa ƙǝm mbuwa wa tǝ ˈya ha, yanɗi nanǝn tǝghǝn ha ƙǝm na nda a thlang nda hai.”
\s1 Karapu aten wiirha na a tsǝrha
\p 
\v 26 Nggǝrgha Yeeso ndaarha, “Na kutǝryid Faara kiya. Niifa washgha wiirha ahu hedghǝn ɗǝ.
\v 27 Mǝngga ha, kyagha wiidɗa sǝ, sǝngwa sǝ tǝ katǝradghǝn hai ƙǝƙǝn wa.
\v 28 Tǝ altenggǝn nagha a tsǝrha, katǝradghǝn hai tǝ kwaafa, ɗǝfgha hur iiwee nǝn.
\v 29 A hǝrǝmɗǝ nakhɗaarha, nǝn a hwasang sǝ tǝ ɗǝhwasarha ƙǝsǝr tsǝ shifiirha hai.”\f + \fr 4:29 \ft Djoyel 3:13\f*
\s1 Karapu aten wiirha na ƙǝla wan parsǝna
\r (Matta13:31-32-34; Luka13:18-19)
\p 
\v 30 Nggǝrgha Yeeso ndaarha, “Tǝ ma nǝm sakh kutǝryid Faara, nduwa tǝ tur yanggi karapu nǝm sakhƙǝn sǝ?
\v 31 Nǝghǝn ƙǝla wan parsǝna na wanggǝn ngguchit ahur wiiya na heu nǝm hǝfrha.
\v 32 A hǝfang ɗǝm hai nǝn tsǝrha tsauka ɗǝfrha manggǝn kal fingya nǝn na ahu hedɗi ǝnagha wuɗikkya ƙǝndan a wuhwaryighǝn.”
\p 
\v 33 Tǝ fingya karapuya ƙǝla yanɗiya hangga thlǝghangna Yeeso kanda sǝ, tǝ fingya na nda mbang sǝnang hai.
\v 34 Mbǝ ˈyasǝ nǝn thlǝghang kanda kula karapu wa. Amma sayidɗi nanǝn tǝ fatsahayighǝn nǝn fǝlanggǝn kanda hai.
\s1 Yanang Yeeso ɓereu ˈyaara
\r (Matta8:23-27; Luka8:22-25)
\p 
\v 35 A farɗi tsǝna figrha hai, ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn, “Tama pǝm wuri aamɗa ɗǝ ya.”
\v 36 Mal fiya nda a samarha, wii nda ɗǝ tǝghǝn ahu kombuwol ɗi nanǝn sǝ. Na fingya kombuwalya sǝ ƙǝm a mbǝɗi mbuwa samadghǝn.
\v 37 Thliigha ɓereu ˈyaara ɓa, nagha a pǝshang aama ahu kombuwol ndan ɓa takhka a timnda hai.
\v 38 Yeeso a ɓeena a samad kombuwol ɗi. Thlengga fatsahayighǝn sǝ ndang ngganda, “Mala, sǝngwa takh ɗǝm a mǝra wa?”
\p 
\v 39 Thliigha Yeeso sǝ, yananggǝn ɓereu ɗi, “Nggasu hai! Ishiu!” Isgha ɓereu ɗi, nggasgha mbǝrha hai.
\p 
\v 40 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn, “Mani tǝrǝm nun? Ai fǝrƙǝkafekkid nun?”
\p 
\v 41 Tǝr ma nda kaan, tsahang mee nda ndan, “Wunniya? Na ɓereurha tǝ kufulla aama fǝrang mamnggirha!”
\c 5
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso niifa na tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa
\r (Matta8:28-34; Luka8:36-39)
\p 
\v 1 Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn ɗǝnda pǝm wuri aamɗa ɗǝ na a chehweed Nggarasina.
\v 2 Tǝrna Yeeso hai ahu kombuwol ɗi, na niifasǝ tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa, kyaghǝn ɓa a mbǝd ten kwaya hwathla Yeeso nǝn fa.
\v 3 Niifɗiya nǝn mǝnda ahur kwad mǝrya, mbǝ niifasǝ na mbang ƙǝnang hai ko tǝ wuyiwurra ni wa.
\v 4 Ƙǝsǝr na nda yakh ƙǝnang nda hai nda harghǝn tǝ sarghǝn tǝ wuyiwurra, amma nǝn ɗahang nda ɗǝ hwasang nggǝn ɗǝɓǝlyina ɗǝ na a sarghǝn. Mbǝ niifasǝ na kanglang na mbang kǝsang hai wa.
\v 5 Nda yanfaara tǝ fǝɗigrha nǝn naarha aten kwaya, tǝ ten ferya, nagha ahuhwaarha tǝ thleng nda fadghǝn ɗǝ tǝ ferya.
\p 
\v 6 Nanǝn Yeeso ɗǝ inggun, ɗagha ɗǝ ɓǝra hai a mbedghǝn.
\v 7 Tǝranggǝn uradghǝn sǝ kaan huhwagha ndǝghǝn, “Mana midwa tǝ nggi, Yeeso, Wan Faara Amshi? Hwanni sa hu thlǝm Faara a sǝsenna wa!”
\v 8 Thlǝk nǝn ndǝn kee ƙǝsǝr ndangga Yeeso, “Kyosǝ a fad niifɗiya, sa ǝnkaheerha!”
\p 
\v 9 Tǝrgha tsahangga Yeeso mee, “Thlǝmwani ƙǝn?”
\p Ndǝghǝn, “Hangga, ƙǝsǝr nan hangga.”
\v 10 Nagha a hwan Yeeso a rǝkɗǝ kanda ma mbǝɗi wa.
\p 
\v 11 Na chiɓǝd ƙǝlengarya sǝ a mbǝɗi a lafrha tsau tǝ sar wumnda fa.
\v 12 Hwangga ǝnkaheeyini Yeeso, “Malang kan ɗan thlǝmad ƙǝlengaryina ɗǝ ya, kyan hur ndan hai.”
\v 13 Nggǝmanggǝn kanda fa, kya nda sǝ a fad niifɗi ɗa nda kyarha ahur ƙǝlengaryina hai. Chiɓǝd ƙǝlengaryini sǝl nda haru kumnggit sǝri, ɗa nda hu wuri aamɗa ɗǝ mǝra nda ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 14 Fa laf ƙǝlengaryini ɗan ndani wupǝri ɗǝ tǝ fingya talya ɗa nda pǝr ǝnɗi katǝragha hai. Ɗagha fiya ɓa, ɓa nda na ǝnɗi katǝragha hai.
\v 15 Ɓana nda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa, na niifɗa nda na tǝ ǝnkaheeyina fa, tsau hai, kalɗǝ lukrha fa ngga ɓa hutenggǝn ɓa, tǝr ma nda.
\v 16 Nafini na a mbǝɗi nagha ǝnɗi katǝragha hai, pǝranggǝn nda kanda ǝnɗi katǝragha hai tǝ niifɗi na tǝ ǝnkahedɗa fa tǝ ƙǝlengaryini ƙǝm.
\p 
\v 17 Tǝrgha nafini hwan Yeeso nda a malanggǝn chehweed ndan.
\p 
\v 18 Na Yeeso a kyarha hu kombuwol hai, niifɗi na tǝ ǝnkahedɗa fa hwan Yeeso nǝn a ɗǝgha ɗǝ a samadghǝn.
\p 
\v 19 Nggǝmangwa Yeeso fa wa, amma ndanggǝn, “Ɗuwa wureɗǝ ɗa wal nafiwa, pǝrang ǝnɗana kanda ǝnona Chinǝm tǝ haɗonǝn fa.”
\v 20 Tǝrgha niifɗi wiigha wureɗǝ ɗǝgha naarha pǝr ǝngya ǝnangna Yeeso a talya kum. Fiya na heu na nda a na ǝnwulteena,
\s1 Nggǝrang Yeeso yibrha wutararha ƙǝfa tǝ ƙǝnang nda nuneefa na faara a ɓang fa
\r (Matta9:18-26; Luka8:40-56)
\p 
\v 21 Nggǝrna Yeeso ɗǝrha pǝm wuri aamɗa ɗǝ tǝ kombuwol, wumngga fiya thlǝmadghǝn ɓa hangga ndǝghǝn ɓalɗǝ a mii wuri aamɗi.
\v 22 Tǝrgha tal ahur mamngya Ƙǝn hwan Faara sǝ na nda aarha Yayirus, ɓa ɗǝ mbǝɗa ɓa. Nanǝn Yeeso ɓǝrgha hai tǝ waɗedghǝn,
\v 23 hwanggǝnǝn, “Wutarad na a mǝra. Niya hwan sa ɓoɓa ɓa ɗǝfang haara teena tǝnǝn ƙǝnda wal yibrha nǝn.”
\p 
\v 24 Ɗǝgha Yeeso ɗǝ a samadghǝn. Fiya hangga mbuwa samadghǝn ɗǝ tǝ ƙǝm na nda a ˈyaɓang mbǝrha fa.
\p 
\v 25 Na nuneefa sǝ a mbǝɗi na faara a ɓang nda fa hai hurarha kumkap sǝri.
\v 26 Sǝsaɗǝ kaan ahar fa fǝr ɗǝfya hangga tǝ ƙǝm ɓǝlang ɗǝ ǝn huharghǝn ɗǝ, a meghedghǝn ˈya kamngga a ƙǝngga amma ƙǝl chikrha.
\v 27 Sǝknǝn laɓar Yeeso, ɓagha ɓa tǝ man samadghǝn ahur fiya tsuwar kootodghǝnǝn fa,
\v 28 ƙǝsǝr numaɗǝ, “A tsuwarɗi kootodghǝn fa kee, niya wal ƙǝnda.”
\v 29 A mbǝɗi tsu kee ishgha farɗi na a ɓang nda fa hai, tǝkƙǝnǝn fa a fadghǝn walɗǝ ƙǝnda ahu sǝsadghǝn.
\p 
\v 30 Tsu sǝnangga Yeeso hai na sǝsǝmnda sǝ kyagha ɗǝ a fadghǝn. Kyahargha hai ahur fiya tsakhmee nǝn, “Wunni tsuwargha kootodna fa?”
\p 
\v 31 Nggǝmangga fatsahayighǝn, “Nanna fiya a ˈyaɓo mbǝrha fa, nana a tsakhmee, ‘Wun tsuwargha nggi fa?’ ”
\p 
\v 32 Amma nagha Yeeso a ƙǝlarha ɗǝ tǝ wunni ǝnagha kee.
\v 33 Tǝrgha nuɗi, sǝnnǝn ˈya katǝragha hai tǝghǝn, ɓagha ɓa ɓǝrgha hai a mbedghǝn, nagha fadghǝn a rǝbrha fa ka tǝrǝmnda, pǝrang ƙǝkafek nǝn ˈya katǝragha hai heu.
\v 34 Ndangga Yeeso nuɗi, “Waana, fǝrƙǝkafekkid wa ƙǝnoɗǝ. Ɗuwaɗǝ hu ɗǝɗemnggirha yibna hu sǝsadwa.”
\p 
\v 35 Yeeso ɓalɗǝ a ndikrha fa kee, ɓagha fingya ɓa a minda ki Yayirus, ndaa nda, “Mǝr wutarad wa, kama nun nggǝr ƙǝtǝlang tǝ malǝmndǝɗa fa?”
\p 
\v 36 Ɗǝfwa Yeeso teena tǝ path nafini wa, ndanggǝn mamnda tǝ Ƙǝn Faara na ngguchit, “A tǝrǝmna wa, furu ƙǝkafek kee.”
\p 
\v 37 Malangwa fiya mbu samadghǝn nda wa, ƙǝl Mbiturus, Yakubu tǝ Yahaya wanman Yakubu.
\v 38 Ɓana nda minda ki mamnda Ƙǝn Faara ɓa na ngguchit, ƙǝlagha Yeeso fiya a tsǝ teena na nda a tǝrha tǝ huhwaarha kaan.
\v 39 Kyanǝn sa hai ndanggǝn kanda, “Kama nda nun a tsǝ teena tǝ huhwaarha kaan kee? Mǝrwa wanɗi wa amma nǝghǝn a shiirha.”
\v 40 Amma masangganda.
\p A kwasamadɗi kyang nǝn fiya ƙǝsha hai, tǝranggǝn nda chin wanɗi tǝ man tǝ fa tsahayighǝn na a thlǝmadghǝn, kyagha hu ƙǝnɗa ɗǝ na wanɗa sǝ.
\v 41 Ƙǝs harghǝnǝn ndanggǝn, “Talita kumi,” ndǝna “Sa wutararha, thliusǝ!”
\p 
\v 42 Thliigha wanɗa sǝ wiigha hai. Huradghǝn kumkap sǝri. Katǝrana ǝnɗa hai ya kanda heu ǝna ǝnwulteena nda.
\v 43 Ƙǝs thlǝman ndan nǝn a sǝk niifa ǝnɗiya wa, ndanggǝn kanda a fǝrang ǝnnarhami nda ǝnagha mii.
\c 6
\s1 Karnda Yeeso a Nadzarat
\r (Matta13:53-58; Luka4:16-30)
\p 
\v 1 Malna Yeeso mbǝɗi, ɗǝgha hu talghǝn ɗǝ tǝ fatsahayighǝn a samadghǝn.
\v 2 Ɓana far yibrha ɓa yi Yahudaya, katǝranggǝn tsaharhaha ahu Ƙǝn Faara na ngguchit, Fiya hangga sǝkka ndǝn ǝna ǝnwulteena na nda, na nda a ndaarha, “Walgha niifɗi ǝnggini a yanggi ya? Tur yanggi sǝnda ni walnǝn, nǝn naarha ǝna ǝnwulteengya kiya?”
\p 
\v 3 “Ndeye, mbǝ kafinta ɗani ya wa? Mbǝ wan Mairamu ni wanmangya Yakubu, tǝ Yisufu, tǝ Yahuda tǝ Siman wa? Wanmanggighǝn nishya mbǝ kulu kǝm tǝ kanda ya wa?” Sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ tǝghǝn.
\p 
\v 4 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Ƙǝl ahur talghǝn, a pathlang hurfayighǝn tǝ hur mindǝghǝn ndǝn mbuwana annabi wal mamnggirha.” \x * \xo 6:4 \xt Yahaya4:44\x*
\p 
\v 5 Ənawa Yeeso ǝnwulteena a mbǝɗi wa, ƙǝl haara ɗǝfang nǝn fingya haaya fa, ƙǝnanggǝn kanda.
\v 6 Fǝrang ɗǝ ǝnwulteena, ka yamid fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan.
\s1 Thlǝn Yeeso kumkap sǝri ɗi
\r (Matta10:5-15; Luka9:1-6)
\p Tǝrgha Yeeso nagha a wiirha hai tala-tala a tsahang fiya ha;
\v 7 Aah kumkap sǝri ɗa nǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, thlǝn kanda nǝn sǝri-sǝri fǝrang sǝsǝmnda nǝn kanda aten ǝnkaheeya.
\v 8 Ndanggǝn kanda, “A turɗun ˈya ahu widɗi ya wa ƙǝl sǝsaala kee. A ƙǝsɗun mburodi ha, ko yawarha, ko wuɗǝɓǝla ahu panjakwayinun wa.
\v 9 Paama pakhma amma ma Kǝsɗun lukrha ha sǝri wa.
\v 10 Kala minda ˈwanun kyarha sahai tsawama sǝ ƙǝl farɗi mal nun talɗi.
\v 11 Kala mbǝrha thlǝwa nanda kun fa, nduwa ƙǝm kangwanda thlǝmarha kun fa wa, a naɗun a mal talɗi tinid talɗi na a sarnun pamanɗǝ ka a tsauka ǝn sakhrha aten ndan\f + \fr 6:11 \ft Luka 10:4-11\f*\f + \fr 6:11 \ft Tar Fathlǝngya 13:51\f*.
\v 12 Ƙya nda ƙǝshaaɗǝ ɗa nda pǝr laɓar Faara a fiya a malangganda ɗimiyid ndan.
\v 13 Kyangganda ǝnkaheeya sǝ hangga a tǝ irang fǝɗeerha fiya fa mbuwa wa ƙǝkanglang ƙǝnangganda kanda.” \x * \xo 6:13 \xt Yakubu5:14\x*
\s1 Mǝrra Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisma
\r (Matta14:1-12; Luka9:7-9)
\p 
\v 14 Sǝkna Hirdus laɓarɗi ya, ƙǝsǝr thlǝm Yeeso ɗǝɗa ɗǝ inggun. Fingya a ndaarha, “Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisma ni thliigha sǝ hu mǝrra, ndǝghǝnni nanǝn tǝ sǝsǝmnda fa yi ǝna ǝnwuteengya.”
\p 
\v 15 Fingya a ndaarha, “Annabi Ilya ni.”
\p Ndagha fingya ƙǝm, “Annabi ni, ƙǝla tal ahur annabiya na kaar.”\f + \fr 6:15 \ft Matta 16:14; Markus 8:28; Luka 9:19\f*
\p 
\v 16 Amma sǝkna Hirdus laɓarɗiya, ndǝghǝn, “Yahaya, niifɗi kyathlangni tenggǝn ɗǝ, thliiɗa sǝ hu mǝrra!”
\v 17 Ƙǝsǝr Hirdus fǝrɗǝ ngyakhrha a ƙǝsangganda Yahaya, muwanggǝn hu porsǝna ɗǝ. Ənanǝn kee ƙǝsǝr ka Herodiya, nu wanman Filibus, kahang nǝn.
\v 18 Ƙǝsǝr Yahaya nǝn naarha ndang nda Hirdus, “Kamngwa a kahangga nu wanmuwa wa.”\f + \fr 6:18 \ft Luka 3:19-20\f*
\v 19 Herodiya sǝb hurghǝn ɗǝ tǝ Yahaya, na midghǝnsǝ a ɓǝlanggǝn amma mbǝ mbang wa.
\v 20 Ƙǝsǝr Hirdus nǝghǝn a tǝrǝm Yahaya, nǝn naarha lafghǝn mbǝ midghǝnsǝ a walgha ˈya ndǝn wa, ƙǝsǝr Yahaya ka niifa ni tǝ peɗǝnda ni. A sǝk Hirdus fad Yahaya nǝn ɓillaghǝn fa kaan, ko nanǝn kee nǝn naarha kang thlǝmarha fa.
\v 21 A kwasamadghǝn wal kwamana nǝn, a farɗi ǝnana Hirdus wutsǝfayid lǝghǝtta ɓen nggǝttǝghǝn hai, aah nǝn mamnggighǝn ɓa tǝ mamngya sodjaya tǝ fingya mamngya na hu chehhweed Nggalili.
\v 22 Tǝrgha wutarad Hirdus kyagha ɓa rǝpgha, mbǝnanggǝn Hirdus tǝ ronggighǝn nana nda a hǝb ǝnnarhami.
\p Ndangga kutǝrɗi wutaradɗi, “Tsahe ˈya na midwa, niya furoƙǝn.”
\v 23 Nggǝmɗa fa har tǝ aah thlǝm Faara, “Kala ˈya tsakhna niya furoƙǝn ko mberra chehweedna ni!”
\p 
\v 24 Ɗǝgha thlǝmad man ɗǝ, ndanggǝn, “Mani tsahang nda?”
\p Ndangga man, “Ten Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisma.”
\p 
\v 25 A mbǝɗi kee thliigha ƙǝkar a thlǝma kutǝra ɗa ɗǝ ndanggǝn, “Na minnasǝ nanǝnya ten Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisma ahu pǝlee.”
\p 
\v 26 Tǝrgha mǝrgha fad kutǝrɗa hai, amma ka ɗǝf miighǝn ǝnanǝn a mbed ronggighǝn, nggǝmngwa fa a hwasanggǝn wa.
\v 27 Tǝrgha thlǝn sodja nǝn ɗǝgha ɓarha ɓa tǝ ten Yahaya. Ɗǝgha ƙǝn porsǝna ɗǝ kyathlanggǝn ten Yahaya hai;
\v 28 ɓagha ɓa tǝ ten Yahaya ahu pǝlee fǝranggǝnǝn wutaradɗa ɗǝ, wutaradɗi ƙǝm fǝranggǝnǝn man ɗǝ.
\v 29 Sǝkna fatsahaya Yahaya ǝnɗi katǝragha hai, ɓa nda ɓa tǝrang ngganda merreghǝn hai pangganda.
\s1 Hǝɓang Yeeso nafiya haru kumnggit tuf
\r (Matta14:13-21; Luka9:10-17; Yahaya6:1-14)
\p 
\v 30 Fathlǝngya Yeeso wuma nda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, pǝrang ǝnggina nda heu ǝnana nda tǝ tsahan ndan ha.
\v 31 Tǝrgha, ƙǝsǝr ka nana fiya hangga na a ɓarha ɓa tǝ fingya a wiirha wal wa Yeeso tǝ fa tsahayighǝn kwaman ǝna ˈya mii wa. Ndanggǝn kanda, “Taama a mbǝrha ɗǝ mbuwana fiyasǝ ƙǝm katen nǝm ɗun yibrha.”
\v 32 Tǝraa nda hu Kombuwol hai katendan ɗǝnda mbǝrha ɗǝ mbuwana fiya sǝ.
\p 
\v 33 Amma fiya hangga nagha kanda a wiirha, kukwalangganda kanda hai ɗa nda ɗǝ tǝ saara tǝ hur talya heu ˈwaa nda mbǝɗa ɗǝ ma kanda.
\v 34 Tǝrna Yeeso hai na fiya nǝn hangga haɗangganda fa, ƙǝsǝr na nda ƙǝla chaukhraya kula tǝ lafrha. Katǝranggǝn tsahang ǝngya kanda ha hangga.\f + \fr 6:34 \ft Ɗeleewar Kirassa 27:17; 1 Kutǝrya 22:17; 2 Laɓarya 18:16; Izikiyel 34:5; Matta 9:36\f*
\v 35 Tsǝna figrha hai, ɓagha fatsahayighǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, ndang ngganda, “Kaheerha ni mbǝɗiya kulo mbiya tsǝ figrha hai.
\v 36 Kalu fiya hai tǝna nda ɗǝrha ahu heeya ɗǝ tǝ talya na tsau a mbǝɗiya ɗa nda kaɗa ǝnnarhami tafan ndan.”
\p 
\v 37 Amma ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Kun tafan nun fǝraman ˈya kanda ǝnna ndami lee.” Ndang ngganda, “Wuɗǝɓǝla na ahar nan nǝn sǝl wuɗǝɓel rapathlaarha na nda teng niifa yi ndǝree wuvaɗa! Ɗan heng mburodi kanda ɓa tǝghǝn fǝranggǝnan kanda ǝna nda mii wa?”
\p 
\v 38 Tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Mburodi kurmi ni ahar nun? A ƙǝla man ɓa.”
\p Wuɗa nda ɓa ndang ngganda, “Mburodi tuf tǝ tǝna sǝri.”
\p 
\v 39 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso fiya a wumangganda tendang tsawa nda hai aten hwalirha.
\v 40 Tǝrgha wumangganda tendan tsawa nda hai fingya kumggit tuf-tuf, fingya haru-haru.
\v 41 Tǝranggǝn mburodi ɗa sǝ tuf tǝ tǝnɗi sǝri, ƙǝlagha talara sǝ, usa Faara nǝn a kyanggǝn mburodi ɗa hai. Fǝranggǝnǝn fatsahayighǝn ndǝghang nggǝnda fiya. Nggǝrghǝn ndǝghang tǝn ɗa hai kowunni walɗǝ.
\v 42 Əna nda mii heu nggaala nda.
\v 43 Wumangga fatsahayighǝn katǝpghǝn kutasya kumkap sǝri heu tǝ tǝnɗi.
\v 44 Hang nda hǝshya ǝnagha mburodi ɗa mii haru kumggit tuf ni.
\s1 Yeeso wiiɗǝ aten aama
\r (Matta14:22-33; Yahaya6:16-21)
\p 
\v 45 Tsu a kwasamad ǝnɗiya, ndangga Yeeso fatsahayighǝn kya nda ahu kombuwol hai ˈwaa nda mbeeɗǝ tǝɗangganda wuri aamɗi teena a Mbatseda ɗe, ndǝghǝnggi ƙǝm kal fiya nǝn hai.
\v 46 A kwasamadɗi kal nǝn fiya hai tǝrgha wumnda sǝ ka ɗǝgha hwan Faara.
\p 
\v 47 Tsǝna figrha hai, kombuwolɗi a maɗufu wuri aamɗi, ndǝghǝn katenggǝn aten chehweerha.
\v 48 Ƙǝlagha Yeeso hai fatsahayighǝn ahu ɓillaarha kaan, ƙǝsǝr ɓereurha a tsang hura kanda fa ahar tsar, ɗǝgha thlǝmad ndan ɗǝ, nagha a wiirha aten wuri aamɗi. Tsǝgha ƙǝla nǝn a mbǝrang kanda hai.
\v 49 Amma nana ndan a wiirha aten wuri aamɗi. Huhwaa nda ka hǝreenga, tamngganda ndaarha mǝnda-mǝnda ni. Huhwaa nda,
\v 50 ƙǝsǝr kanda heu nandan tǝr ma nda. Inanggǝn mighǝn hai ƙǝkar ndanggǝn kanda, “Ƙǝrsaama, nggini. A tǝrǝmɗun wa.”
\v 51 Tǝrgha kyagha ahur kombuwol ɗa hai tǝ kanda, nggasgha ɓereu ɗa hai. Ƙǝsgha ǝnwulteena kanda,
\v 52 ƙesǝr ɓalgha nda kula sǝnang ǝnwulteena ɗa hai ǝnana Yeeso aten mburodi ɗi, ƙǝsǝr ka kakrakkit tendan.
\v 53 Tǝɗang nanda wuri aamɗi teena, sǝla nda Djanisǝrat ɗǝ, ƙǝnangganda kombuwol ndan hai.
\v 54 Kyana nda sǝ ahur kombuwol ɗi, kukwalangga fiya Yeeso hai.
\v 55 Ɗa nda hai ahu chehwedɗi kahad na nda a ɓarha ɓa tǝ haaya ahu ɗǝnggǝlya kala mbǝrha sǝknanda na Yeeso sǝ.
\v 56 Kala mbǝrha ɗǝna Yeeso sa ɗǝ, hu talya tǝ wupǝri tǝ kaheeya na nda hunang haaya hai hu kasu hwanggǝnda a tsuwar pǝpǝshaprha kaɓadghǝn nda fa. Kala niifa tsuwargha ndǝn fa wal ɗǝ ƙǝnda.
\c 7
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten pǝpedyid hura
\r (Matta15:1-9)
\p 
\v 1 Farɗa sǝ ɓagha fingya Farisaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha a Urshalima ɓa, wuma nda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa.
\v 2 Ƙǝla nda hai fingya fatsahaya Yeeso kanda a hǝb ǝnnarhami haryi ndan tǝ “Paarha”, ndǝna haryi ndan kula tsaɓrha ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 3 Ƙǝsǝr Farisaya tǝ Yahudaya mba nda hǝb ǝnnarhami kanda kula tsaɓang har ndan ɗǝ wa, ƙǝs nda ǝntin shingya ha.
\v 4 Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm mba nda kii ˈya hiina nda ɓa ahu kasu wa ƙǝl tsaɓang na nda haryi ndan ɗǝ ˈwan. Na ǝntingya sǝ ƙǝm hangga na nda lafrha, ƙǝla tsab ɗengya tǝ ɓǝǝya tǝ tasaukya tǝ ɓaleeya tǝ ǝnfuya.
\p 
\v 5 Tǝrgha Farisayini tǝ famalǝngya ngyakhrha tsahang mee nda Yeeso, “Kama mbuwana fatsahayiwa takkwa ǝntin shingginǝm, na nda a ǝna ˈya mii tǝ har paaya?”
\v 6 Nggǝmangga Yeeso kanda, Kun fa thlǝrɓuya! A ten nun ni thlǝkna annabi Ishaya pathɗiya, ƙǝla nanǝn chichireethlee hai tǝ ndaarha,
\q1 “‘Nafiniya, ahu mii ndan ni kee na nda fǝre mamnggirha,
\q2 amma hur yi ndan nǝghǝn inggun ma nggi;
\q1 
\v 7 ka ni kee na nda a tǝree shilee teena,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr ɗǝfangganda tsahad ǝntina a mbee,
\q2 ma ˈya ndana Faara.’”\x * \xo 7:7 \xt Ishaya29:13\x*
\b
\p 
\v 8 “Malanggun ˈya ndana Faara ƙǝs ǝntina nun ha ǝnana chichiyi nun.”
\p 
\v 9 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Kar ngyakhrha Faara nun fa ka a laf ngyakhrha ǝntin chingginun nun!
\v 10 Ƙǝsǝr ndagha Musa, ‘Fǝrang mamnggirha nda muwa tǝ tsu,’ tǝ ƙǝm, ‘Kala niifa ˈyargha chin nduwa man na nda ɓǝlang nda.’
\v 11 Amma nduwun, a ndang niifa chin nduwa man, ‘ˈYa niya kya ɗang nda kunsǝ, ˈwaɗi teena ɗǝfangɗi ndǝn Faara ɗǝ,’
\v 12 tǝrgha mbun malang niifɗiya ɗanggǝn chin sǝ nduwa man wa.
\v 13 Tsawanggun laɓar Faara mbǝ ˈya ni na ngga wa, ka ǝntin ngginun. Nun naarha ǝna ǝngya kee hangga.”
\s1 ˈYa na tsawang nda niifa tǝ ɗimiyirha fa a mbed Faara
\r (Matta15:10-20)
\p 
\v 14 Fiya wumngga hai nggǝrgha Yeeso aah kanda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, ndanggǝn kanda, “Keema thlǝmarha fa kun heu, a sǝn ǝnɗanun ya.
\v 15 ˈYa na a ƙǝshi kyagha hur niifa ɗǝ mbǝ ndǝna tsawang tǝ paarha wa, amma ƙǝl ˈya na a kyarha sǝ ahurghǝn ndǝna tsawang nda tǝ paarha fa.
\v 16 Yi na tǝ thlǝmad sǝkrha sǝkƙǝnǝn.”
\p 
\v 17 A kwasamadɗi malna Yeeso fiya kyanǝn hur minda hai, fatsahayighǝn tsahang mee nda ha aten karapu ɗi ya.
\v 18 Tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Sǝnanggun hai wa? Mbun a naghǝn wa ˈya kyagha hur niifa ɗǝ a ƙǝshi mbǝ ndǝna tsawang nda tǝ paarha fa wa?
\v 19 Ƙǝsǝr kyawa ahurghǝn hai wa amma ahu mbǝbǝlǝmndǝghǝn ɗǝ, nggǝrghǝn kyarha sǝ a fadghǝn.” (Thlǝk nǝn pathɗiya a kyad ndaarha nǝn ǝnnarhami heu na nda ngga.)
\p 
\v 20 Ɗǝgha mbeeɗǝ tǝ ndaarha, “ˈYa na a kyarha ɓa ahur niifa ndǝna tsawang nda tǝ ‘paarha fa’.
\v 21 Ƙǝsǝr ahur niifa sǝ, ndǝna numad ǝn mbǝlfeeya kyarha ɓa, susuwayirha, ngaara, ɓǝl farha, kulafayirha,
\v 22 kwit hura, mbǝlfeerha, nggaɓarha, suna, sǝrǝkkirha, sǝb thlǝma, nggǝm alteena, tǝ yamid huteena.
\v 23 Ən mbǝlfeeyini na heu ya na nda kyarha sǝ ahur niifa; nǝn tsawang niifa ‘ɗimirha.’ ”
\v 24 Tǝrgha Yeeso mal Nggalili nǝn ɗǝgha hu chehweed Taya ɗǝ tǝ Sidon. Kyagha hur minda hai mbǝ midghǝn sǝ a sǝngga fiya sǝ wa, amma mbǝ mbang ɓǝɓeng ɓadghǝn ɓa wa.
\v 25 A mbǝɗi kee, nuneefa sǝ na wutaradghǝn tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa, sǝknǝn laɓar Yeeso ɓagha ɓa ɓǝrgha hai a mbedghǝn.
\v 26 Nuɗi tǝ Helenarha ni, nggǝtgha ndan a Fǝnikiya a chehweed Suriya. Hwan Yeeso nǝn a kyanggǝn ǝnkaheedɗa sǝ a fad wutaradghǝn.
\p 
\v 27 Ndangga Yeeso, “Malang wundakhnaya ˈwan nggaala nda, ƙamngwa tǝranggǝm ǝnnadmid wundakhnaya fǝranggǝnǝm wuɗaya wa.”
\p 
\v 28 Ndangga nuɗi Yeeso, “nǝghǝn kee, Chinǝm, amma na wuɗaya ǝna fǝfǝsǝrra ǝnnarhami na a hǝra hai ahar wundakhnaya.”
\p 
\v 29 Ndangga Yeeso, “Ƙǝsǝr ka laɓarɗi kyawa nggǝreena sǝ ya, wiu fayiwa, ǝnkaheedɗi kyaɗa sǝ a fad wutarad wa.”
\p 
\v 30 Ɗǝgha nuɗi wure ɗǝ ɗǝgha wal wutaradɗi keeghǝn kath hu sǝra, ɗǝkɗa hai tǝ ǝnkaheedɗi.
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso Niifa na teɓeng tǝ tip
\p 
\v 31 Tǝrgha malgha Yeeso chehweed Taya kyagha tǝ chehweed Sidon tǝ chehweerha na tǝ Talya Kum ɗǝgha wuri aam Nggalili ɗǝ.
\v 32 Na nafiya sǝ ɓagha ɓa tǝ niifa a Yeeso na teɓeng tǝ ƙǝm mbǝ mbang kaala sǝ wa. Hwanggǝnda a ɗǝfang haara nǝn teena.
\p 
\v 33 Ɗǝgha Yeeso tǝ teɓeng ɗi man patu ɗǝ ma fiya, panggǝn wan haryighǝn ahu thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ. Chakh yakhrha nǝn hai, tsuwar sheneu niifɗa nǝn.
\v 34 Ƙǝlagha Yeeso talara sǝ yibgha fa kaan ndanggǝn, “Ifata!” Ndǝna “Inuɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 35 Tǝrgha ingga thlǝmad niifɗa ɗǝ, kwasgha sheneuƙǝn hai nagha a ndikrha fa ngga.
\v 36 Ndangga Yeeso kanda a pǝrang ndan niifa wa. Amma ndǝghǝn aten yanang kanda, kanda aten pǝrghǝn ɗǝ.
\v 37 Ƙǝsgha ǝnwulteena fiya kaan na nda a ndaarha, “Ənaɗǝ ǝngya heu ngga, ƙǝnanggǝn teɓengya tǝ fingya mbuwa mbang kalasǝ.”
\c 8
\s1 Yeeso hǝɓang fiya haru kumnggitghǝn faɗa
\r (Matta15:32-39)
\p 
\v 1 Na farɗa sǝ nggǝrgha fiya wumnda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa, nanǝn mbǝ ǝnnarhami sǝ ahar ndan wa, aagha Yeeso fatsahayighǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ndanggǝn kanda,
\v 2 “Na nafini a haɗee fa ya. Ɓeena mahan kanda a thlǝmanna, takhkwa ˈya ahar ndan a ǝna nda mii wa.
\v 3 A kal ɗi kanda hai wii nda wureeɗǝ a miirha, ɗǝna nda fǝla hai a kwamana. Ƙǝsǝr ɓagha fingya ɓa a mbǝrha ɓa inggun.”
\p 
\v 4 Ndangga fatsahayighǝn, “Amma ɗǝnǝm wal ǝnnarhami ɓa a yanggi a kahedɗiya na tsǝghang kanda?”
\p 
\v 5 Tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Mburodi kurmi ahar nun”?
\p Ndang ngganda, “Mǝd.”
\p 
\v 6 Ndanggǝn fiya a tsawa nda hweeɗe hai. Haranggǝn mburodiɗa sǝ mǝd, hwan parka Faara nǝn, kyanggǝn hai fǝranggǝnǝn fatsahayighǝn ɗǝ a ndǝghang nggǝnda fiya ɗǝ, ǝna nda kee.
\v 7 Tǝna sǝ ahar ndan ngguchit ƙǝm, hwan parka Faara nǝn atenggǝn, ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn a ndǝghangganda ɗǝ.
\v 8 Ənagha fiya mii nggaala nda. Akwasamadghǝn wumangga fatsahayighǝn kwasamadghǝn kutasya mǝd.
\v 9 Hǝshya ǝnanda haru kumnggitghǝn faɗa. Kal nǝn kanda hai,
\v 10 kyagha ahur kombuwol hai tǝ fatsahayighǝn ɗǝgha a chehweed Ɗalmanuta ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 11 Ɓagha Farisaya ɓa katǝrang ngganda tsahang mee Yeeso ha. Ka a ƙǝƙǝrangganda, tsahang mee nda ha a kyad ǝnsakhrha nǝn a talara hai.\f + \fr 8:11 \ft Matta 12:38; Luka 11:16\f*
\v 12 Yibgha fa ndǝghǝn, “Mani na nafiya ƙǝshiid weeriya a kaɗa ǝnsakhrha yi wulteena? Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, mbǝ ǝnsakhrha sǝ nanda a kyatta wa.”\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Matta 12:39; Luka 11:29\f*
\v 13 Tǝrgha mal kanda nǝn, wudgha ahur kombuwol hai tǝɗagha man patu ɗǝ.
\s1 Mehen Farisaya tǝ yi Hirdus
\r (Matta16:5-12)
\p 
\v 14 Fatsahaya Yeeso mbǝɗang ɗǝ kanda ɓawa nda ɓa tǝ mburodi wa, ƙǝl tal ni kee ahur kombuwol ɗi.
\v 15 Ƙǝsgha Yeeso thlǝmandan ndǝghǝn, “Kwarama tǝ mehen Farisaya tǝ yi Hirdus.”\f + \fr 8:15 \ft Luka 12:1\f*
\p 
\v 16 Tsǝ laɓara nda atenggǝn a pathlang ndan, ndanda, “Ƙǝsǝr mbuwana mburodi sǝ ahar nǝm.”
\p 
\v 17 Yeeso sǝnang ɗǝ numan ndan hai ndanggǝn kanda, “Kama nun tsǝ laɓara tǝ ndaarha mbǝ mburodi sǝ ahar nun wa?
\v 18 Kun tǝ yirha mbun a naghǝn wa, tǝ thlǝman nun sǝ mbun a sǝkƙǝn wa? Ɓal wun kula sǝnang hai wa?\f + \fr 8:18 \ft Irmiya 5:21; Izikiyel 12:2; Markus 4:12\f*
\v 19 Kyang ni mburodi ɗa hai tuf a fiya haru kumnggitghǝn tuf, Kutasya kurmi wumang nun kwasamadghǝn?”
\p Ndang ngganda, “Kum kap sǝri.”
\p 
\v 20 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Kyang ni mburodi ɗa hai mǝd a fiya haru kumnggitghǝn faɗa, kutasa kurmi wumang nun katǝpghǝn?”
\p Ndang ngganda, “Mǝd.”
\p 
\v 21 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Sǝnanggun hai wa?”
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso kwamarha a Mbatsaida
\p 
\v 22 Ɓa nda Mbatsaida ɓa, ɓagha nafiya ɓa tǝ kwamarha hwan Yeeso nda a tsuwarghǝnǝn fa.
\v 23 Ƙǝs har kwamadɗa nǝn kya nda sǝ ma hur talɗi ɗǝnda ƙǝsǝr talɗa ɗǝ. Chakh nǝn yakhrha a yid niifɗa ɗǝ ɗǝfang haara nǝn fa, tsahangga Yeeso mee, “Na ˈya sǝ nana wa?”
\p 
\v 24 Ƙǝlagha sǝ ndǝghǝn, “Nggi a na fiya, na nda ƙǝla ɗǝfya a wiirha hai.”
\p 
\v 25 Nggǝrgha Yeeso ɗǝfang harghǝn a yid niifɗa ɗǝ. Tǝrgha ingga yidghǝn ɗǝ, nggǝrgha yidghǝn ɓa, nagha a ƙǝlarha ɗǝ ngga.
\v 26 Wuɗangga Yeeso wureeɗǝ, ndanggǝn, “A nanna a wutta wureeɗǝ a kyanna hur talɗa hai ya wa.”
\s1 Mbiturus fǝrɗǝ ƙǝkafek Yeeso ndǝna Ƙǝrǝsti
\r (Matta16:13-20; Luka9:18-21)
\p 
\v 27 Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn ɗǝnda hu talya ɗǝ a Kaisariya Filibi. Nana nda a wiirha hu kwamana tsahangga Yeeso mee fatsahayighǝn, “Na fiya a ndaarha wunni nggi?”
\p 
\v 28 Ndang ngganda, “Fingya a ndaarha Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisǝma, fingya a ndaarha Ilya ni, fingya a ndaarha ƙǝm, nǝghǝn tal ahur annabiya.”
\p 
\v 29 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Amma kun wu, nuwun a ndaarha wunni nggi?”
\p Ndangga Mbiturus, “Sani Ƙǝrǝsti.”\f + \fr 8:29 \ft Yahaya 6:68-69\f*
\p 
\v 30 Ƙǝsgha Yeeso thlǝmandan a pǝrang ndan niifa tǝ wunni ndǝghǝn wa.
\s1 Thlǝk Yeeso kwaman mǝrrǝghǝn
\r (Matta16:21-28; Luka9:22-27)
\p 
\v 31 Katǝranggǝn tsahang kanda ha tǝ ndaarha Wan niifa tǝtani a sǝsaagha aten ǝngya hangga, na shingya, tǝ mamnda firistaya, tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha a karghǝn fa, nanda a ɓǝlang nda akwasamad ɓeena mahan nǝn a nggǝr thliirha sǝ.
\v 32 Thlǝkƙǝn pathɗiya a pǝpal.
\p Ɗǝgha Mbiturus tǝghǝn man patu ɗǝ ndanggǝn mǝmǝlwa nagha a thlǝk ˈya kiya wa.
\p 
\v 33 Amma kyahargha Yeeso hai ƙǝlanggǝn fingya fatsahayighǝn ɗǝ yanaggǝn Mbiturus, ndǝghǝn, “Nduwu hai tǝ nggi sa Sheetan, mba a ƙǝlang ǝngya na mid Faara wa, amma ǝngya kee na mid fiya.”
\p 
\v 34 Tǝrgha aah fiya nǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa heu tǝ fatsahayighǝn ndanggǝn kanda, “Ana mid niifa sǝ mbu samanna nǝn malanggǝn nggǝm altenggǝn tǝranggǝn kaɗidghǝn sǝ, mbu samadna nǝn.\f + \fr 8:34 \ft Matta 10:38; Luka 14:27\f*
\v 35 Ana mid niifa sǝ ɗǝf yiɓǝdghǝn ɗǝ nǝn ƙǝɗeng nda. Amma kala niifa fǝrgha yiɓǝdghǝn ka nggi tǝ yi laɓarɗi na mbǝnggǝn ya ɗǝfang nǝn ɗǝ.\f + \fr 8:35 \ft Matta 10:39; Luka 17:33; Yahaya 12:25\f*
\v 36 Ma chighang nǝn niifa a walɗǝ ǝn ƙǝshiirha heu ƙǝɗenggǝn yiɓǝdghǝn?
\v 37 Nduwa ƙǝm mana niifa fǝra a meghed yiɓǝdghǝn?
\v 38 A shiɗangwa niifa tǝ laɓarna ahu ƙǝshiid kulafayirha tǝ ɗimiyirha wa, Nggi, na Wan Niifa, mbǝ shiɗeerha ka ndǝghǝn wa a ɓaɗǝ hu mamnggit Chin ɓa tǝ yi fathlǝngya Faara tǝ peɗǝnda.”
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn kanda, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, na fingya sǝ ƙǝkǝt a mbǝɗiya nanǝnya mba nda a taarang mǝra fa wa na nda a naa Kutǝryid Faara ɓayi tǝ sǝsǝmnda mamnggitghǝn.”
\s1 Kyaharra fad Yeeso hai
\r (Matta17:1-13; Luka9:28-36)
\p 
\v 2 Akwasamad ɓeena mikki tǝrangga Yeeso Mbiturus tǝ Yakubu tǝ Yahaya tǝraa nda wumnda sǝ, kanda katendan. A mbǝɗi kyahargha fadghǝn hai a mbed ndan.
\v 3 Lukkighǝn kyakhra nda hai pǝpet, pǝpettǝghǝn kalɗǝ mbǝrha mu hu ƙǝshidɗiya.
\v 4 Tǝrgha kyagha nda Ilya ɓa tǝ Musa katǝrang ngganda ndikrha hai tǝ Yeeso.
\v 5 Ndangga Mbiturus Yeeso, “Mala, nǝghǝn ngga nanǝm a mbǝɗiya, ngwa ǝna chama nan mahan-tal yiwa, tal yi Musa tǝ ƙǝm tal yi Ilya.”
\v 6 Sǝngwa ˈya nǝn a thlǝkrha, ƙǝsǝr kanda heu tǝrǝmnda kaan.
\p 
\v 7 Tǝrgha ɓagha hashbe ɓa nggǝlanggǝn kanda, sǝk urarha nda hai ahur hashbiɗi tǝ ndaarha, “Waana niya, nggǝmni. Kaman thlǝmarha fa!”\f + \fr 9:7 \ft 2 Mbiturus 1:17-18\f*
\v 8 Kula sǝndǝndan sǝ, ƙǝla nda hai ko niifa ɓal, ƙǝl Yeeso katenggǝn.
\p 
\v 9 Na nanda a tǝraa hai a wumndǝɗi, ƙǝsgha Yeeso thlǝmandan a pǝrang ndan niifa ˈya na nanda wa ƙǝl ma thlid Wan Niifa sǝ ahu mǝrra.
\p 
\v 10 Nanǝn kee ƙǝsghǝnda ha ahur ndan, na nda a ndang nda ndan tǝmani “Thliirha sǝ hu mǝrra.”
\p 
\v 11 Tsahang mee nda ha, “Mani na famalǝmngya ngyakhrha ndaarha tǝta Ilya ni a ˈwa ɓaarha ɓa?”\f + \fr 9:11 \ft Malachi 4:5; Matta 11:14\f*
\v 12 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Ƙǝkafekni, Ilya ni a ˈwa ɓarha ɓa, ka ɓagha tangsang ǝngya ɗǝ heu. Kama nda chireethleng nanda hai Wan Niifa tǝtani a sǝsaagha tǝ ƙǝm karghǝnda fa?
\v 13 Amma niya ndang nda kun, ɓa Ilya ɓa, ǝnang ǝngya nda fa tǝrna mindan, ƙǝla nanǝn chichirethlee hai atenggǝn.”\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Matta 17:13\f*
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso Wundǝlaarha na tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa
\r (Matta17:14-21; Luka9:37-43a)
\p 
\v 14 Tǝrnanda hai, ɓa nda wal fingya fatsahaya, ƙǝla nda hai wum fiya thlǝmandan ɓa tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha kanda a ngaala tǝ kanda.
\v 15 Hǝrǝmna fiya na Yeeso, tǝk mbǝnda nda fa ɗaa nda ɗǝ ɗa nda ndangˈya.
\p 
\v 16 Tsahangga Yeeso mee fatsahayighǝn, “Mani nun a ngaalang teena tǝ kanda?”
\p 
\v 17 Ndagha niifa ahur fiya ɓa, “Mala, ɓoni waana ɓa, nǝghǝn tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa har ˈyaɗang ɗǝ ndikrha fa.
\v 18 A thliiɗa ɓa, nǝn muwang hweeɗa hai. Nagha miighǝn a hufrha fa, nagha a ƙǝt miighǝn hwargha fadghǝn ɗǝ. Kalangɗi fatsahayiwa sǝ, amma mbang ngwanda wa.”
\p 
\v 19 Ndangga Yeeso, “Kun wangya ƙǝshiid weeriya fa yamid fǝrƙǝkafekkya, pa kwanɗǝ ni tsaurha tǝ kun? Pa kwanɗǝ ni naarha tǝ kun? Ɓee wanɗa ɓa.”
\p 
\v 20 Ɗang wanɗa nda ɗǝ. Nana ǝnkaheedɗi Yeeso, muwanggǝn wundǝladɗi a hweeɗa hai nagha fadghǝn a rǝprha fa tǝ miighǝn a hufrha hai.
\p 
\v 21 Tsahangga Yeeso mee chin wundǝladɗi, “Ɓeena kurmi ndǝghǝn tǝghǝn kiya?”
\p Ndagha chin wanɗi, “Ka ndǝghǝn ngguchit.
\v 22 Na ǝnkaheedɗi naarha muwang hu waarha hai tǝ aama ka a ɓǝlanggǝn. Amma a nanna a mbangnda a haɗowan fa ɗang kansǝ.”
\p 
\v 23 Ndagha Yeeso, “‘A nanna a mbangnda’? ˈYa na heu nǝghǝn pǝpa a fad niifa fǝrgha ƙǝkafek.”
\p 
\v 24 Ƙǝkar ndagha chin wanɗi, “Fǝrɗi ƙǝkafek, amma ɗeesǝ tǝna fǝrƙǝkafekkid na chikrha!”
\p 
\v 25 Ƙǝlana Yeeso hai fiya a ɗaarha ka ƙǝlarha ɓa, yananggǝn ǝnkaheedɗi, ndanggǝn, “Sǝsǝn teɓeng tǝ tip, ndoyi kyosǝ a fad wanɗiya a Nggǝrna kyarha fadghǝn hai ɓalwa!”
\p 
\v 26 Tǝrgha ǝnkaheedɗi huhwaagha nagha wanɗi a tsǝˈya fa kaan a kyagha sǝ. Tsauka wanɗi kǝla mǝrra, kowunni a ndaarha, “Mǝrɗǝ.”
\v 27 Amma ƙǝsgha Yeeso harghǝn sǝ, thliigha sǝ ƙǝt.
\p 
\v 28 A kwasamadɗi kyana Yeeso wure hai, tsahangga fatsahayighǝn mee ɓǝɓee, “Mani mbangwa nan kyang ǝnkaheedɗa sǝ?”
\p 
\v 29 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Tur yanɗiya ƙǝl tǝ hwan Faara ndǝnǝn kyarha sǝ.”
\s1 Nggǝr Yeeso ndikrha aten mǝrrǝghǝn
\r (Matta17:22-23; Luka9:43b-45)
\p 
\v 30 Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn malangganda mbǝɗi kya nda tǝ Nggalili. Mbǝ midghǝn sǝ a sǝngga fiya mbǝɗi nanǝn sǝ wa,
\v 31 ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn a tsahang fatsahayighǝn ha tǝ ndaarha, “Wan Niifa na nda a fǝrghǝn ahar nafiya hai. Na nda a ɓǝlang nda. A kwasamad ɓeena mahan nǝn a nggǝr thliirha sǝ.”
\v 32 Amma sǝnangwanda tsahadɗa ha keeghǝn ya wa, kanda ƙǝm a tǝrǝm tsahang mee.
\s1 Wunni Manggǝn?
\r (Matta18:1-5; Luka9:46-48)
\p 
\v 33 Ɓa nda Kafarnahum ɓa, nana nda ahur minda, tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Mani nun a ngaalang teena a kwamana?”
\p 
\v 34 Amma nggasa nda hai tǝtip ƙǝsǝr a kwamana na nda a ngaala aten wunni manggǝn.\f + \fr 9:34 \ft Luka 22:24\f*
\p 
\v 35 Tsauka Yeeso hai, aah kumkap sǝri ɗanǝn ɓa, ndanggǝn kanda, “Kala niifa na midghǝn sǝ a tsauka a mbee, tǝtani tsauka a samaarha heu tǝ mafad kowunni.”\f + \fr 9:35 \ft Matta 20:26-27; 23:11; Markus 10:43-44; Luka 22:26\f*
\p 
\v 36 “Tǝranggǝn wundakhnee ɓa ishanggǝn a maɗufun ndan. Ƙǝs harghǝnǝn ndanggǝn kanda,
\v 37 Kala niifa thlǝgha wundakhnee fa ngguchit ƙǝla yanɗiya ahu thlǝmna thlǝnǝn nggi fa, tǝ ƙǝm kala niifa thlǝgha nggi fa thlǝnǝn Pǝpa fa thlǝngga nggi ɓa.”\f + \fr 9:37 \ft Matta 10:40; Luka 10:16; Yahaya 13:20\f*
\s1 Kala niifa mbuwa tsan ƙǝm yinǝm ni
\r (Luka9:49-50)
\p 
\v 38 Ndangga Yahaya Yeeso, “Mala, na ɗan niifa a kyang ǝnkaheeya sǝ tǝ thlǝmwa, yanang ɗan ƙǝsǝr mbǝ ahur nǝm wa.”
\p 
\v 39 Ndangga Yeeso, “A yanang ɗun wa, ƙǝsǝr kala niifa ǝnagha ǝnwulteena tǝ thlǝmna akwasamadghǝn mbǝ thlǝk ǝngya mbuwa ngga atenna wa.
\v 40 Kala niifa mbuwa tsan ƙǝm, yinǝm ni.\f + \fr 9:40 \ft Matta 12:30; Luka 11:23\f*
\v 41 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, kala niifa fǝrangga aam saarha kun ko ahu wuhuleurha tal ahu thlǝmna ƙǝsǝr ka tsaunun yina mbǝ tam ƙǝɗeng wal ƙǝnaghǝn wa.\f + \fr 9:41 \ft Matta 10:42\f*
\s1 Ɗimiyirha tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek
\r (Matta18:6-9; Luka17:1-2)
\p 
\v 42 “Ana niifa sǝ kyangga tal ahur wangginiya hu ɗimiyirha hai, A nggushi waghang nda fǝn hǝrha ura mughang ngganda ahu wuri aama ɗǝ.
\v 43 Ana harwa a kyorha hu ɗimiyirha hai, kyathlang ɗǝ, a nggushi kyana hu kutǝryid talara ɗǝ tǝ haara tal ma kyana hu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai tǝ haara sǝri.
\v 44 A mbǝɗi waya na naarha kii kanda mba nda mǝra wa, wadɗi ƙǝm mba nda mbang ɓǝlang hai wa.\f + \fr 9:44 \ft Matta 5:30\f*
\v 45 Ana sarwa a kyorha hu ɗimiyirha hai, kyathlang ɗǝ. A nggushi kyana hu kutǝryid talara ɗǝ tǝ saara tal ma kyana hu waarha ɗǝ tǝ saara sǝri.
\v 46 A mbǝɗi waya na naarha kii kanda mba nda mǝra wa, wadɗi ƙǝm mba nda mbang ɓǝlang hai wa.
\v 47 Ana yidwa kyorha hu ɗimiyirha hai, ƙǝɗang ɗǝ. A nggushi kyana hu kutǝryid talara ɗǝ tǝ yirha tal ma kyana hu waarha ɗǝ tǝ yirha sǝri.\f + \fr 9:47 \ft Matta5:29\f*
\v 48 A mbǝɗi,
\b
\q1 ‘Wayini na kii kanda mba nda mǝra wa,
\q2 wadɗi ƙǝm mba nda mbang ɓǝlang hai wa.’”\f + \fr 9:48 \ft Ishaya66:24\f*
\b
\p 
\v 49 “Kala niifa na nda a tsaɓang nda ɗǝ tǝ waarha ƙǝla na nda tsaɓang sataka ɗǝ tǝ fǝsa.” \x * \xo 9:49 \xt Livitikus2:13\x*
\p 
\v 50 “Fǝsa nǝghǝn ngga, amma a tǝr mbǝndǝghǝn ɗǝ, tǝma nǝm nggǝr nggǝrang ɓa? Naama tǝ fǝsa fa, tǝ ƙǝm naama ɗǝɗem tǝ ndan,”\f + \fr 9:50 \ft Matta 5:13; Luka 14:34-35\f*
\c 10
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten ɓǝlla kakhrha
\r (Matta19:1-12; Luka16:18)
\p 
\v 1 Tǝrgha malgha Yeeso Kafarnahum, ɗǝgha chehweed Yahuda ɗǝ tǝ pǝm kufad Urdun. Nggǝrgha fiya naarha wumnda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, tsahanggǝn kanda ha ƙǝla nǝn tǝ ǝnaarha.
\p 
\v 2 Ɓagha fingya Farisaya ɓa na mindan sǝ a ɗǝfang takthleera nda. Tsahang mee nda ha, ndang ngganda, “Pǝranggǝn kan, ahu ngyahad nǝm mǝmǝlni a kalgha niifa nukkun hai?”
\p 
\v 3 Tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Ndagha ɗeleewar Musa ƙǝn?”
\p 
\v 4 Ndang ngganda, “Ndagha ɗeleewar Musa a chirethlengga niifa ɗeleewar nǝn nukkun sǝ kalghǝnǝn hai.”\f + \fr 10:4 \ft Ɗeleewar Nggurub Ngwa kumarha24:1-4; Matta5:31\f*
\p 
\v 5 Amma nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, ndǝghǝn, “Ka kakrakid tennun ni ndangna Musa kun kee.
\v 6 Amma a katǝra ǝna ƙǝshiirha, ‘Faara ǝnaɗǝ hǝshneefa tǝ nuneefa.’ \x * \xo 10:6 \xt Katǝrarha1:27; 5:2\x*
\v 7 Ndǝn ǝnagha ndǝn na niifa mal chin tǝ man thlǝthlǝɓanggǝn nukkun fa,
\v 8 sǝri ɗi nanda tsau thlu farha tal. Ɓalwanda sǝri ɓalwa, amma tsau nda tal.\f + \fr 10:8 \ft Katǝrarha2:24\f*
\v 9 Tsaunǝn kee mbǝ niifa sǝ na ndǝghang ˈya hai wumangna Faara wa.”
\p 
\v 10 Wudnanda hur minda hai, nggǝrgha fatsahayini tsahang mee Yeeso aten laɓarɗiya.
\v 11 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Kala niifa kalgha nukkun hai kakhka pak ǝnanǝn kulafayirha aten nuɗi.
\v 12 Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm, kala nuneefa ndǝkka hai tǝ chimadghǝn, nggǝrghǝn kakh chimarha pak ǝnanǝn kulafayirha.”\f + \fr 10:12 \ft Matta 5:32; 1 Korontiyaya 7:10-11\f*
\s1 Ɗǝfang Yeeso parka wundakhnaya teena
\r (Matta19:13-15; Luka18:15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Na farɗasǝ ɓagha fiya ɓa tǝ wanggindan ka a ɗǝfangga Yeeso parka kanda teena, amma fatsahayighǝn na nda a yanang kanda.
\v 14 Amma nana Yeeso ǝnɗi na nda a ǝnaarha, sǝbgha hurghǝn ɗǝ ndanggǝn kanda, “Malaman wundakhnaya na nggun-ngguchit ɓa nda thlǝmanna ɓa, a yanang ɗun kanda wa. Ƙǝsǝr Kutǝryid Faara yi tur ndanni.
\v 15 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, kala niifa thluwawa kutǝryid Faara ƙǝla na wundakhnee ngguchit ǝnaarha wa mbǝ tam kyaarha saɗǝ wa.”\f + \fr 10:15 \ft Matta 18:3\f*
\v 16 Tǝrgha tǝranggǝn wanggini a fad pǝniyighǝn sǝ ɗǝfang haara nǝn kanda teena fǝrang parka nǝn kanda.
\s1 Tǝ ƙǝna
\r (Matta19:16-30; Luka18:18-30)
\p 
\v 17 Thliina Yeeso wiirha, ɗagha niifa thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ɓǝrgha hai tǝ waɗedghǝn a mbedghǝn ndanggǝn, “Ka tǝmalǝmnda, ma kamngga tǝta a ǝnee tǝni wal yibrha mbuwa ngwalarha?”
\p 
\v 18 Ndangga Yeeso, “Mani na aah nggi ka niifa? Mbǝ ka niifa sǝ wa ƙǝl Faara katenggǝn.
\v 19 Sǝnna ˈya ndaana ngyakhrha, ‘A ɓǝlna farha wa, a ǝnanna kulafayirha wa, a ngaarna wa, a nggaɓangna niifa fa ka wa, a huk na farha wa, fǝrang mamnggirha nda muwa tǝ tsu,’ ”\f + \fr 10:19 \ft Kyarhaɓa20:12-16; Ɗeleewar nggurub Ngwa Kumarha5:16-21\f*
\p 
\v 20 Ndangga niifɗi Yeeso, “Mala, ka nggi ngguchit lafɗi ngyakhkini ya.”
\p 
\v 21 Ƙǝlangga Yeeso niifɗi tǝ yid nggǝmnda ndanggǝn, “Taho ˈyaha tal kamngga a ǝnana, ɗuwaɗǝ ɗa heng ǝnggiwa ɗǝ heu nana tǝghǝn ha fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝlghǝna fa yamiiya, na wal mbǝd ɗǝfǝdghǝn a talara. Tǝrgha a ɓana ɓa, ɓa mbu samadna.”
\v 22 A mbǝɗiya sǝbgha hur niifɗaɗǝ, wiigha tǝ hurghǝn sǝsǝɓa ɗǝ ƙǝsǝr tǝ ƙǝnani kaan.
\p 
\v 23 Kyahargha Yeeso hai ƙǝlagha ɗǝ, ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn, “Nǝghǝn pǝɗaghǝn a kyagha tǝ ƙǝna ahu kutǝryid Faara ɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 24 Sǝkna Fatsahayini pathɗi kee fǝrang ǝnwulteena nǝn kanda. Amma nggǝrgha Yeeso ndang kanda, “Wanggina, nǝghǝn pǝɗaghǝn kaan, na a kyagha niifa hu kutǝryid Faara ɗǝ.\f + \fr 10:24 \ft Pǝɗaghǝn\ft Fingya chireelthya yi kaar chik ndan tǝ “tǝƙǝna” nduwa “yanɗi mbǝrsagha tǝ ƙǝna.”\f*
\v 25 Nǝghǝn pǝpa a kyagha thlǝkhmu ɗǝ tǝ kwad libra ma tǝ ƙǝna kyagha hu kutǝryid Faara ɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 26 Nggǝrgha pathɗi chighang ǝnwulteena fatsahayini na nda a tsahang mee ndan ha, “Anaɗǝ kee wunni a wal hǝrǝkrha?”
\p 
\v 27 Ƙǝlangga Yeeso kanda ɗǝ ndǝghǝn, “Niifa tǝ wasa in nǝghǝn pǝɗaghǝn, amma mbǝ tǝ Faara wa, ƙǝsǝr ǝngya heu nǝghǝn pǝpa a fad Faara.”
\p 
\v 28 Tǝrgha ndangga Mbiturus, “Malang ɗan ǝngya heu mbuɗan samadwa.”
\p 
\v 29 Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, mbǝ niifa sǝ malangga wurighǝn nduwa wan manggighǝn hǝshya nduwa wan manggighǝn nishya nduwa man nduwa chin nduwa wanggighǝn nduwa heeyighǝn ka nggi tǝ laɓar Faara
\v 30 na ƙǝɗeng wal ƙǝnaghǝn katǝra haru aten, wuraya, wan mangya hǝshya, wan mangya nishya, mangya, waya tǝ kaari-tǝ sǝsaaya. A hu ƙǝshiirha na ɓayi na nda a wal yibrha mbuwa ngwalarha.
\v 31 Amma fingya ˈwagha kanda ni a nggǝl mee, fingya nggǝlgha mee kanda ni a ˈwaarha.”
\s1 Nggǝr Yeeso thlǝk kwaman mǝrrǝghǝn
\r (Matta20:17-19; Luka18:31-34)
\p 
\v 32 Kanda hu kwaman ɗǝrha Urshalima ɗǝ, Yeeso a mbee, fatsahayighǝn a na ǝnwulteena, fiya na a mbusamad ndan ƙǝm ƙǝsgha hǝreenga kanda. Nggǝrghǝn ɗǝrha tǝ fatsahayighǝn man patu ɗǝ pǝrang ˈya nǝn kanda ɗǝgha katǝrarha hai tǝghǝn.
\v 33 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗǝnǝm Urshalima ɗǝ, ɗǝna nda fǝr Wan Niifa a mamnda firistaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha. Na nda a ngwang kumad mǝrra fǝranggǝnda fingya mbuwa Yahudaya.
\v 34 Na nda a waaghǝn, chahang yakhrha nda fa, tsaɗaghǝn nda, ɓǝlangganda. A kwasamad ɓeena mahan nǝn a nggǝr thliirha sǝ.”
\s1 Hwandǝn nda Yakubu tǝ Yahaya
\r (Matta20:20-28)
\p 
\v 35 Tǝrgha nda Yakubu tǝ Yahaya wangya Dzabadi, ɓa nda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ndang ngganda, “Mala, na minnan sǝ a ɗangga kansǝ.”
\p 
\v 36 Tsahang mee nǝn kanda, “Mana minnun a ǝnanggi kun?”
\p 
\v 37 Nggǝrangganda sǝ, “A ɗǝd na hu tsǝnggam kutǝryidwa ɗǝ ngwa tsauka tal ahur nan a yisǝmadwa tal ƙǝm a yikawadwa.”
\p 
\v 38 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ ndǝghǝn, “Sǝnggun ˈya nun a hwanda wa! Nun mbang saarha tǝ wuhuleuɗi niya saarha sǝ wa nduwa ǝnang mbaptisǝma nda kun tǝ tur mbaptisǝma ǝneena nda wa?”
\p 
\v 39 Ndang ngganda, “Haˈi, nan a mbang nda.” Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Nun a mbang saarha tǝ wuhuleu sanna tǝ ƙǝm ǝnang mbaptisǝma nda kun tǝ tur mbaptisǝma ǝneena nda,
\v 40 amma tsaurha a yisǝmadna tǝ yikawadna mbǝ nggini fǝrghǝn wa. Mbǝyini ya yi fingya ni ngwagha fa.”
\p 
\v 41 Tahad fingya kum sǝknanda kee, sǝbgha hurndan ɗǝ aten nda Yakubu tǝ Yahaya.
\v 42 Nanǝn kee, aagha Yeeso kanda ɓa heu ndǝghǝn, “Sǝnɗunsǝ fingya tsauka kutǝrya fiya hu ƙǝshidɗiya mbuwa Yahudaya sǝnna nda kanda tǝ kutǝryirha, fingya mamngya ƙǝm kanda ni tǝ sǝsǝmnda ha heu aten fingya na a kamu ndan.
\v 43 Amma ahur nun nǝn a tsaurha pak. Kala niifa na midghǝn tsauka ndǝghǝnni mamnda tǝta ni tsauka ƙǝla mafad nun.\f + \fr 10:43 \ft Luka 22:25-26\f*
\v 44 Kala niifa na midghǝn a nagha a mbee, tǝtani a tsauka mafad kowunni.\f + \fr 10:44 \ft Matta 23:11; Markus 9:35; Luka 22:26\f*
\v 45 Ko nggini na Wan Niifa, ɓawi ɓa mbǝ ka a ǝnee taara nda wa, amma ka ǝnang taara ni fingya tǝ ƙǝm fǝr yiɓǝd nani a meyed fiya hangga.”
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso kwamarha
\r (Matta20:29-34; Luka18:35-43)
\p 
\v 46 Tǝrgha ɓa nda Djeriko ɓa. Nana Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn heu tǝ fiya na a mbusamad ndan a kyarha sǝ ahur talɗi, na kwamarha sǝ tsau a mii kwamana a hwanda thlǝmnggǝnni Mbartimawus wan Timawus.
\v 47 Sǝknǝn ndaarha Yeeso tǝ Nadzarat ni na a mbǝraɗǝ, katǝranggǝn huhwaarha hai, “Yeeso! Wan Ndauda! A haɗoyi fa!”
\p 
\v 48 Fiya hangga njarghǝnda, ndang ngganda, “Nggasu hai.”
\p 
\v 49 Sǝkna Yeeso ndǝn, ishgha hai ndǝghǝn, “Ndaman a ɓagha ɓa.”
\p Aaghǝn nda, ndang ngganda, “No wutsǝfayirha fa, thliusǝ nǝghǝn a aah sa.”
\v 50 Tǝrgha kwamadɗi pǝrgha sǝ, muwanggǝn kootodghǝn ɗǝ, ɗǝgha thlǝmad Yeeso ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 51 Tsahangga Yeeso mee, “Mana midwa a ǝnoyi?”
\p Ndangga kwamadɗi, “Mala, na minnasǝ a namanani hai.”
\p 
\v 52 Ndangga Yeeso, “Ɗuwaɗǝ, fǝrƙǝkafekkid wa ƙǝnoɗǝ.”
\p Tsu a mbǝɗi kee na mana nǝn hai mbusamad Yeeso nǝn.
\c 11
\s1 Thlǝd fiya Yeeso fa tǝ wutsǝfayirha a Urshalima
\r (Matta21:1-11; Luka19:28-40; Yahaya12:12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Takhna Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn a ndusang Urshalima fa, ɓa nda Mbetafaji ɓa tǝ Mbetani na a Wumngya Ɗǝfya Dzaitun, thlǝngga Yeeso sǝri ahur fatsahayighǝn a ˈwa nda mbeeɗǝ.
\v 2 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗaama ahu talɗa ɗǝ na a mbennun taarha, a kyaɗun sahai, nun a na wan kwaara ƙǝƙǝna hai ˈwawana nanda tǝraa. Kwasaman hai, ɓon ɓa tǝghǝn.
\v 3 A tsahang niifa mee kun, ‘kama nun a ǝnaarha kee?’ ndaman, ‘Chinǝm ndagha na midghǝnsǝ nǝn a wuɗang ɓa wed.’ ”
\p 
\v 4 Ɗǝgha fatsahayina ɗǝ ɗa nda wal wan kwarɗi a mii kwamana, ƙǝƙǝna hai a kwatkirma. Na nanda a kwasang hai,
\v 5 nafiya na ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗi tsahang mee nda kanda, “Ma nun a ǝnaarha, kama nun a kwasang wan kwarɗa hai?”
\p 
\v 6 Pǝr ǝnɗa nda thlǝghangna Yeeso kanda, malangga nafini kanda.
\v 7 Ɓang wan kwarɗa nda Yeeso ɓa muwangganda parkoyindan a ƙǝsǝrghǝn sǝ.
\v 8 Fiya hangga lǝlǝɓangganda kootoyindan hai ahu kwamana, fingya kyath shiiya nda ɓa lǝlǝɓangganda hai.
\v 9 Nagha fiya na a samadghǝn tǝ yi mbedghǝn ahuhwaarha,
\b
\q1 “Falama Faara!
\q2 Tǝ parkani niifɗi ɓagha ɓa ahu thlǝm Chinǝm!\f + \fr 11:9 \ft Dzabura 118:25-26\f*
\q1 
\v 10 Parkani kutǝryidɗi na ɓayi
\q2 yi chichit nǝm Ndauda.
\q1 Falama Faara
\q2 na a talara!”\f + \fr 11:10 \ft Samaila 7:11-14\f*
\p 
\v 11 Ɗǝna Yeeso Urshalima ɗǝ kyagha ahu Ƙǝn hwan Faara ɗǝ. Ƙǝlanggǝn mbǝya heu, amma tsaunǝn hǝm yanfaara hai, kyagha sǝ tǝ fatsahayighǝn ɗǝnda Mbetani ɗǝ.
\s1 Shiwang Yeeso ɗǝf shiɓarha
\r (Matta21:18-19)
\p 
\v 12 Ɗathna mbǝrha hai na nanda a mal Mbetani, nagha miirha a ƙǝs Yeeso.
\v 13 Ƙǝla nǝn ɗǝ na ɗǝf shiɓarha nǝn ɗǝ tǝ shee fa, ɗǝgha kamughǝn ɗǝ ƙǝlanggǝn tǝnǝn wal wanggǝn. Ndusang nǝn fa, mbǝ ˈyasǝ wal nǝn a uradghǝn wa ƙǝl shiiya, ƙǝsǝr shifidghǝnni wa.
\v 14 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn ɗǝfǝdɗi, “A nggǝr niifa kii ɗǝfǝd wa ɓalwa pakwanɗǝ.” Sǝkka fatsahayighǝn ˈya ndanǝn.
\s1 Rǝghang Yeeso fa shafiliya ɗǝ a Ƙǝn Faara
\r (Matta21:12-17; Luka19:45-48; Yahaya2:13-22)
\p 
\v 15 Sǝlna Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn a Urshalima ɗǝ, kyagha a pǝpal Ƙǝn Faara ɗǝ ƙatǝranggǝn rǝghang nda nafiya ɗǝ na a ǝna shafili a mbǝɗi. Chaggǝlanggǝn tebǝrya fa mbeɗed wuɗǝɓǝla tǝ kulohod fa heng kataprakkya,
\v 16 mbǝ malang niifa mbǝrgha ɗǝ tǝ ǝn shafili tǝ pǝpal Ƙǝn Faara wa.
\v 17 Tsahanggǝn kanda ha ndǝghǝn, “Nǝghǝn chichirethlee hai ahu ɗeleewar Faara tǝ ndaarha,
\q1 “‘Ƙǝnna nǝm aaghǝn
\q2 Ƙǝn Faara yi fiya heu.’
\q1 Amma tsawanggun mbǝd ɓǝɓed ngaarya.”\x * \xo 11:17 \xt Ishaya56:7; Irmiya7:11\x*
\b
\p 
\v 18 Mamnda firistaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha sǝk nanda ǝnɗi katǝragha hai katǝrang ngganda kaɗa kwamana hai na a ɓǝlangganda. Amma kanda a tǝrǝmnggǝn, ƙǝsǝr fiya heu tsahadghǝn ha nǝghǝn a fǝrang ǝnwulteena kanda.
\p 
\v 19 Tsǝna figrha hai, Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn kya nda sǝ a wupǝri ɗi.
\s1 Tsaharhaha aten shiɓadɗi
\r (Matta21:20-22)
\p 
\v 20 A tsar, na nanda a wiirha, na shiɓadɗa nda hwarɗaɗǝ tǝ thlaryighǝn.
\v 21 Ɗalghǝna Mbiturus ndǝn in ndanggǝn Yeeso, “Mala! Kuloɗǝ! Ɗǝfǝd shiɓadɗi shiwangna na!”
\p 
\v 22 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso fatsahayini, “Fǝrama ƙǝkafek a Faara.
\v 23 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, a ndang niifa wumndǝɗi ya, ‘Ɗǝwaɗǝ, ɗa muwang fadwa a wuri aama ɗǝ,’ a ngaal wa ahurghǝn wa amma fǝrɗǝ ƙǝkafek tǝ ndaarha ˈya thlǝknǝn nǝn a katǝrarha hai, nanda a ǝnanggǝn.\f + \fr 11:23 \ft Matta 17:20; 1 Korontiyaya 13:2\f*
\v 24 Tsaunǝn kee niya ndang nda kun, kala ˈya na minnun a hwanang ɗun Faara, tǝ ƙǝkafekkirha, nun a walghǝn.
\v 25 A naɗun a hwan Faara, ˈwaama teena chahang ɗimiyid ndan nun fingya ɗǝ ǝnangga ɗimiyirha kun fa, tǝna yinun Chiina na a talara chahang ɗimiyid nun kun ɗǝ.
\v 26 Amma a chakhkun ɗimiyirha wa, mbǝ yinun Chiina na a talara a chahang ɗimiyid nun kun ɗǝ wa.” \x * \xo 11:26 \xt Matta6:14-15\x*
\s1 Mamngya Yahudaya tsahang nda mee Yeeso
\r (Matta21:23-27; Luka20:1-8)
\p 
\v 27 Nggǝrna Yeeso ɓaarha Urshalima ɓa, ndǝghǝn a wiirha hai a pǝpal Ƙǝn Faara, Mamnda firistaya, famalǝmngya ngyakhrha tǝ shingya ɓaa nda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa.
\v 28 Tsahang mee nda, “Tǝ tur yanggi ngyahadyi na ǝna ǝngginiya, wun furowa kwaman ǝna ǝnɗiya?”
\p 
\v 29 Nggǝmangga Yeeso kanda, “Niya tsahang mee kun ha tal. A nggǝreeɗun sǝ, niya pǝranggǝn kun tǝ wun fǝreegha kwamana niya ǝna ǝngginiya.
\v 30 Wun fǝrangga kwamana Yahaya ǝna mbaptisǝma nǝn? Faara fǝrangga wa, nduwa fiya wa? Pǝreemadghǝn!”
\p 
\v 31 Tǝrgha thliigha ngaala sǝ a pathlang ndan, ndaa nda, “A ndaa ɗǝm, ‘a talara ni hai,’ nǝn a tsakh mee, ‘Kama fǝrangwa nun ƙǝkafek?’
\v 32 A ndaa ɗǝm, Fiya fǝrangga.” Na nda a tǝrǝm fiya, ƙǝsǝr sǝn fiya sǝ Yahaya annabini.
\v 33 Ndang ngganda Yeeso, “Sǝngwan wa.”
\p Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Nggi ƙǝm mbi pǝranggǝn kun tǝ wunni fǝreegha ngyakhrha niya ǝna ǝngginiya wa.”
\c 12
\s1 Karapu aten nafiya huɗagha hu hed niifa
\r (Matta21:33-46; Luka20:9-19)
\p 
\v 1 Katǝrangga Yeeso laɓara hai tǝ karapuya, ndǝghǝn, “Na niifa sǝ ǝnagha hed wan ɗǝfya, kanggǝn raa mbǝd ˈyaɗa wan ɗǝfyina nǝn tǝ ƙǝm tǝn mbǝd ƙǝla hedɗa nǝn ɗangkam. Dzǝmanggǝnǝn fahuɗaya ha ɗǝgha hu chehweerha ɗǝ inggun.” \x * \xo 12:1 \xt Ishaya5:1-2\x*
\p 
\v 2 Tsǝna shifirha hai thlǝn mafadghǝn nǝn thlǝmad nafina ɗǝ nzǝmngga hedɗi a ǝnang wan ɗǝfyina nda ha.
\p 
\v 3 Amma nafini nzǝmngga hedɗi ɗǝghangganda mafadɗa ɗǝ wuɗangganda ko ˈya a harghǝn.
\v 4 Nggǝrghǝn thlǝnang mafarha kanda ɗǝ, ɗǝkƙǝn nda atenggǝn fǝrang shilee nda.
\p 
\v 5 Yi mafarha nggǝrnǝn thlǝnda ɗǝ ɓǝlangganda. Ɗǝgha mbeeɗǝ tǝ thlǝn mafayighǝn ɗǝ fingya ɗǝk kanda nda, fingya ɓǝlangganda kanda.
\p 
\v 6 “Tahanggǝn ha tal nǝn a thlǝnda, wanggǝn nggǝmnǝn kaan. Thlǝnanggǝn wanggǝn a thlǝmad ndan ɗǝ, ahu numadghǝn, ‘Ɗǝna nda fǝrang mamnggirha waana.’”
\p 
\v 7 “Amma ndangga fahuɗayini ndan, ‘Kulo tǝ har langad hedɗi ɓayiya, tama ɓǝlanggǝm tǝna hedɗi tsaurha yinǝm ya!’
\v 8 Nanǝn kee, ƙǝsangganda wan ɗa ɓa ɓǝlangganda muwangganda ƙǝshaaɗǝ ma hedɗi.”
\p 
\v 9 Tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Ma kamngga a ǝnagha tǝ hedɗi? Nǝn a ɓarhaɓa ɓǝlanggǝn nafina ɗǝ dzǝmngga hedɗi fǝrang hedɗa nǝn nafiya pak.
\v 10 ˈWawun karatang ǝnɗiya ahu ɗeleewar Faara wa?
\b
\q1 ‘Feera karna fa tǝngya
\q2 ndǝn tsauka fer sar ƙǝnna.
\q1 
\v 11 Ənɗa ǝnana Faara ya,
\q2 Nadghǝn ǝnwulteena ni.’”\f + \fr 12:11 \ft Dzabura 118:22-23\f*
\b
\p 
\v 12 Tǝrgha kaɗa kwamana nda na a ƙǝsangganda ƙǝsǝr sǝndasǝ a tendan ni ǝnanǝn karapuɗiya. Amma kanda a tǝrǝm fiya; nanǝn kee malangganda wii fayindan nda.
\s1 Tii tsamnda a Kaisar
\r (Matta22:15-22; Luka20:20-26)
\p 
\v 13 Kanda sǝ, thlǝn Farisaya nda tǝ nafiya Hirdus a thlǝmad Yeeso ɗǝ a ɗǝfang takthleera nda tǝ pathya tǝna nda ƙǝsang nda tǝ pathla ɗimi.
\v 14 Ɓaa nda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ndang ngganda, “Mala, sǝnɗansǝ ka niifa ni sa, Sa mba wurahasǝ wa fiya heu yiwa ni, Sa na thlǝk ƙǝkafek. Kamɗǝ ateng tsamnda nan Kaisar wa nduwa awo?
\v 15 A ten wa nduwa awo?”
\p Amma Yeeso sǝnɗǝ thlǝrɓuyindan, ndanggǝn kanda, “Kama nda nun a ɗǝfee takthleera? Fǝree ma pene ɗa ɓa ƙǝlanggi.”
\p 
\v 16 Ɓang pene ɗa nda ɓa, tsahang mee nǝn kanda, “Shishing nda wunni tǝ thlǝm wunni atenggǝn?”
\p Ndang ngganda, “Yi Kaisar ni.”
\p 
\v 17 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Fǝraman ˈya Kaisar tsauka yi Kaisar, a Faara tsauka yi Faara.”
\p Əna ǝnwulteena nda tǝghǝn.
\s1 Tsakhmee aten thliirha sǝ ahu merra tǝ kakhrha
\r (Matta22:23-33; Luka20:27-40)
\p 
\v 18 Tǝrgha Sadukiyaya ɓa nda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa kanda ndagha mbǝ thliirha sǝ hu mǝra wa tǝ tsakhmee, \x * \xo 12:18 \xt Tar fathlǝngya23:8\x*
\v 19 ndang ngganda, “Mala, chireethleng Musa ndǝn kan hai tǝ ndaarha a mǝr wan man niifa mal nuneefa nǝn hai amma kula wundakhnaya, tǝtani a kahangga wan man nuu mǝrɗi ka a nggǝɗang waya nǝn wan mansǝ.\f + \fr 12:19 \ft Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 25:5\f*
\v 20 Nanǝnya na wan mangya sǝ mǝd. Tǝpamǝnda kahanggǝn mǝrgha kula nggǝt wundakhnaya.
\v 21 Yi sǝri kahanggǝn nu mǝrɗi, amma mǝrgha kula mal wee hai. Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm tǝ yi mahan.
\v 22 Kanda heu mǝd kahang nda nuɗi mǝra nda kula kanda mal wundakhnaya hai. A kwasamadghǝn nuɗi ƙǝm mǝrgha.
\v 23 Nanǝnya, ahu thliirha sǝ hu mǝrra na nuɗi tsaurha yi wun, tsaunǝn nafini mǝd kahang nda?”
\p 
\v 24 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, ndǝghǝn, “Numad nun mbǝ mǝmǝl wa ƙǝsǝr sǝnggun Laɓar Faara na chichireethlee hai tǝ sǝsǝmnda Mamnggitghǝn wa.
\v 25 A far thliirha sǝ hu mǝra, na nda tsaurha ƙǝla fathlǝngya Faara mba nda kakhrha wa.
\v 26 Nanǝnya aten thlid mǝrya sǝ, a ɗeleewar Musa, karatanggun laɓar nji waarha na a kaheerha ndangna Faara, ‘Nggini Faara yi Ibrahim, tǝ Ishaku tǝ ƙǝm Yakubu’ wa? \x * \xo 12:26 \xt Kyarhaɓa3:6\x*
\v 27 Ndǝghǝnggi mbǝ Faarani yi mǝrya wa, amma yi fa yibya ni, kun sahadɗun kaan!”
\s1 Ngyakhrha na manggǝn
\r (Matta22:34-40; Luka10:25-28)
\p 
\v 28 Niifa tal ahur famalǝmngya ɗeleewar Musa ɓagha ɓa ɓagha wal kanda a ngaala. Ƙǝlanǝn hai nggǝrang Yeeso kanda sǝ mǝmǝl, tsahang mee nǝn Yeeso, “A hu ngyakhkya heu, yanggini manggǝn?”
\p 
\v 29 Ndangga Yeeso, “Yanɗi na manggǝn nǝghǝn kiya, ‘Sǝghamadghǝn, kun Isǝreela! Chinǝm Faarnǝm ndǝghǝnni Chinǝm katenggǝn.
\v 30 Nggǝmu Chinǝm Faarwa, tǝ hurwa heu, tǝ yiɓǝdwa heu tǝ huten wa heu, tǝ kanglanggid wa heu.’ \f + \fr 12:30 \ft Ngwa Kumarha 6.4\f*
\v 31 Yi na a takkwaghǝn ndǝna, ‘Nggǝmu tuladwa ƙǝla altenwa.’ Mbǝ ngyakhrha sǝ kalgha finayiniya wa.” \f + \fr 12:31 \ft Livitikus 19.18\f*
\p 
\v 32 Tǝmalǝmnda ɗeleewar Musa ɗi ndanggǝn Yeeso, “Mala, thlǝknan mǝmǝl. Thlǝkna ƙǝkafek ndana Faara tǝtal mbusǝ pak wa.\f + \fr 12:32 \ft Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 4:35\f*
\v 33 Na a nggǝmnggǝ nǝm, tǝ hurnǝm heu, yiɓǝd nǝm heu, tǝ kanglanggid nǝm heu, tǝ kǝm nggǝmu tuladwa ƙǝla altenwa ndǝna manggǝn na nji satakh maɓiya tǝ fingya satakhkya.”\f + \fr 12:33 \ft Hodzaya 6:6\f*
\p 
\v 34 Nana Yeeso kamshiiɗi nggǝrang ɗa sǝ ngga tǝ ndǝdǝlyirha ndanggǝn, “Mbaa inggun tǝ kutǝryid Faara wa.” A mbǝɗi kee nggǝrwa niifa tsahang mee ɓalwa.
\s1 Tsakh Yeeso mee aten Ƙǝrǝsti
\r (Matta22:41-46; Luka20:41-44)
\p 
\v 35 Nana Yeeso a tsaharhaha a pǝpal Ƙǝn Faara, tsakh mee nǝn, ndǝghǝn, “Mani na famalǝmngya ngyakhrha ndaarha Ƙǝrǝsti wan Ndauda ni?
\v 36 Ndauda tafadghǝn, nanǝn lǝlǝgɗa tǝ Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda ndǝghǝn,\f + \fr 12:36 \ft Dzabura 1101\f*
\q1 “‘Chinǝm ndanggǝn Yina China,
\q2 Tsawu a yisǝmanna
\q1 ƙǝl a tsawangɗi fa tsanggiwa,
\q2 a kamu saryiwa.’”\f + \fr 12:36 \ft Dzabura 110:1\f*
\b
\m 
\v 37 “Ndauda tafadghǝn aaghǝn ndǝn, ‘Chinǝm.’ Ƙǝƙǝn nǝn tsaurha wanggǝn?”
\p Fiya wumngga hai na nda a kang thlǝmarha fa tǝ wutsǝfayirha.
\s1 Yeeso yanangɗǝ Famalǝngya ngyakhrha
\r (Matta23:1-36; Luka11:37-54; 20:45-47)
\p 
\v 38 A hu tsahadghǝn ha, ndǝghǝn, “Kwarama tǝ famalǝngya ngyakhrha. Kanda na mindansǝ kal kaɓaya fa ana nda a wiirha hai a yid fiya tǝ ƙǝm anagha fiya a ndangˈya kanda ahu kasu.
\v 39 Na nda naarha wur mbǝd tsaukya na nggǝngga a ƙǝngya tsahad Yahudaya tǝ mbǝd mbǝnafa.
\v 40 Na nda naarha huk nu mǝrya ahu wurayindan. Na nda djib hwan Faara tǝna fiya ndaarha ka nafiya ni kanda. Tur nafiniya na Faara sǝsang kanda kaan ma fingya.”
\s1 Fal Yeeso fǝrra nu mǝrra
\r (Luka21:1-4)
\p 
\v 41 Tǝrgha Yeeso tsauka tsau tǝ mbǝɗi na panjakwadɗa sǝ nagha a ƙǝlang kanda a Ƙǝn Faara. Fa ƙǝnaya hangga fǝr nda wuɗǝɓǝlya manggǝn.
\v 42 Tǝrgha ɓagha nu mǝrra ɓa tǝ yamirha fǝr yighǝn nǝn anini sǝri.
\p 
\v 43 Aah fatsahayighǝn nǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, ndanggǝn kanda, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, fǝrrǝɗi kii nu mǝrɗiya kalɗǝ yi fiya heu.
\v 44 Nafini na heu ya fǝrghanda ahu hangnda ˈya na nanda tǝghǝn ha, amma ndǝghǝn nggi ahu yamidghǝn fǝrɗǝ ˈya na a harghǝn heu.”
\c 13
\s1 Əngya na a katǝrarha hai a mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha
\r (Matta24:1-2; Luka21:5-6)
\p 
\v 1 Na Yeeso a kyarha sǝ ahu Ƙǝn Faara, tal ahur fatsahayighǝn ndanggǝn, “Mala! Ƙǝlang feryini na mǝmanggǝn sakhɗang nanda tǝnggina sǝ ya! Tur tǝngginiya ǝnwulteena ni!”
\p 
\v 2 Ndangga Yeeso, “Nanna tǝnggini na nggǝngga ya? Nanda a chaggǝnlang kanda hai, mbǝ feera sǝ nanda a malang aten shadghǝn wa.”
\s1 Katǝra sǝsaarha
\r (Matta24:3-14; 21:7-19)
\p 
\v 3 Nana Yeeso tsau a mbǝd ɗǝfya Dzaitun kang hura nǝn Ƙǝn Faara fa, Nda Mbiturus, tǝ Yakubu, tǝ Yahaya tǝ Andǝrawus tsahang mee nda Yeeso ha ɓǝɓee, ndang ngganda,
\v 4 “Akwan na ǝnggini a katǝrarha hai ya? Mani ǝn sakhrǝghǝn na a kyat lǝghǝttǝghǝn nǝn?”
\p 
\v 5 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Kwarama naɗǝ niifa sakhɗang kun.
\v 6 Fiya hangga na a ɓarha ɓa hu thlǝmna, na nda a ndaarha kanda ni ‘nggi,’ naa nda a sakhɗang fiya hangga.
\v 7 A sǝkɗun yangya tǝ fiya a tsǝ laɓar yangya, a tǝrǝm ɗun wa. Tsauɗǝ tǝtani a katǝragha hai, amma mii ngwaladghǝn ɓalɗǝ ˈwan.
\v 8 Na chehweeya yanda tǝ ndan, kutǝrya ƙǝm na nda yanda tǝ ndan. Na chehweerha a rǝprha fa a mbǝya hangga, tǝ miirha. Əngginiya katǝra sǝsaarha ni ˈwan.”
\p 
\v 9 Amma kwarama. Ƙǝsǝr na nda a ɗǝrha tǝ kun mbed mamngya ɗǝ na ahu ƙǝngya tsahad Yahudaya tsaɗa kun nda, tǝ ƙǝm muwangganda kun ahu porsǝna ɗǝ. Nanda a ɗǝrha tǝ kun a mbed ngwamnaya ɗǝ tǝ kutǝrya ka thlǝmna. Ənɗaniya na fǝrang kwamana kun pǝr ƙǝkafek nun atenna.
\v 10 Laɓarɗi na mbǝnggǝn ya tǝtani pǝrghǝnɗa hu ƙǝshiirha ɗǝ heu.
\v 11 Amma a ƙǝsang nda kun a ɓillaɗun tǝ ˈya nun a thlǝkrha ka a hǝrghanggun fannun wa. Thlǝghaama ǝnɗi ndangna Faara kun kee, ƙǝsǝr mbǝ kunni na a kaala sǝ wa, amma Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda ni.\f + \fr 13:11 \ft Matta 10:17-20; Luka 12:11-12\f*
\p 
\v 12 “Na wan maana a fǝr wan man ɓǝlangganda, chiina ƙǝm nǝn a fǝr wanggǝn. Wundakhnaya na nda a thleng chinggindan fa ka a ɓǝlangganda kanda.
\v 13 Na fiya heu a kar kun ƙǝsǝr ka nggi, amma kala niifa ƙǝrǝsgha ta mii ngwalarha ɗǝ nǝn a hǝrǝkrha.”\f + \fr 13:13 \ft Matta 10:22\f*
\s1 Sǝsaarha na pǝɗaghǝn
\r (Matta24:15-28; Luka21:20-24)
\p 
\v 14 “Na sayi ɓayi ɓanun naa ‘Ən tsangya na ɓarha ɓa tǝ ndǝkrha hai’ ƙǝt a mbǝrha kamngwa wa. Tǝrgha fingya na a Yahudiya a ɗaarha wumngya sǝ.\f + \fr 13:14 \ft Ndaniyel 9:27; 11:31; 12:11\f*
\v 15 Niifa na aten ƙǝnna mbǝ tǝra hai kyagha ƙǝnɗǝ ka a ngwagha fa wa.”
\p 
\v 16 Niifa na a hee a wudɗǝ ndaagha ɗǝnǝn tǝrang kootodghǝn wa.
\v 17 Kawa ma nishya na ahur tǝ fingya na tǝ waaya ƙǝsǝr a faryiniya!
\v 18 Hwanama Faara a katǝra ɗa hai ahu mbiirha wa.
\v 19 Ƙǝsǝr na sǝsaarha a naarha sǝ kaan ˈwawanda ǝnaarha, ka ǝnana Faara ƙǝshiirha ta hu sayidɗa ɓa ya. Tǝ ƙǝm mba nda nggǝr ǝna turghǝn wa.\f + \fr 13:19 \ft Ndaniyel 12:1; Tar Fathlǝngya 7:14\f*
\v 20 A mbǝnana Faara thleng ɓengginiya wa, mbǝ niifa sǝ na takh tǝ yibrha wa. Amma ƙǝsǝr ka nafiyighǝn na wuwura, ndǝn tsang nǝn ɓenggini hwas.
\p 
\v 21 “A sayidɗiya a ndon niifa, ‘Kulo Ƙǝrǝsti ya,’ nduwa ‘Kulo ndǝghǝn taarha,’ a kangna thlǝmaarha fa wa.
\v 22 Ƙǝsǝr na fa nggaɓaya Ƙǝrǝsti sǝ tǝ yi annabiya na a thliirha sǝ ǝna ǝnwuteengya nda ka a sakhɗang ngganda fiya heu tǝ fingya na wuwura yi Faara, a naɗǝ a kya naarha sǝ.
\v 23 Nanǝn kee, kwarama ƙǝsǝr ˈwaɗi teena pǝrangɗi ndǝn kun.”
\p 
\v 24 “A akwasamad sǝsadɗi,
\q1 “‘Na yanfaara a tsaurha wulghǝn,
\q2 ndǝree ƙǝm mbǝgha njaara hai wa.\f + \fr 13:24 \ft Ishaya 13:10; Izikiyel32:7; Djoyel 2:10; 3:4; 3:15; Tar Fathlǝngya 6:12\f*
\q1 
\v 25 Na wufǝlgaarya a mukrha hai a fǝrakh amshi,
\q2 ǝngya na mǝmanggǝn a talara na nda a tsǝˈyafa.’”\f + \fr 13:25 \ft Ishaya13:10, 34:4; Djoyel2:10; Tar Fathlǝngya6:13\f*
\p 
\v 26 “A farɗi na fiya a naa Wan Niifa ɓayi ahu hashbe tǝ sǝsǝmnda tǝ mamnggitghǝn.\f + \fr 13:26 \ft Ndaniyel 7:13; Tar fathlǝngya 1:7\f*
\v 27 Nǝn a thlǝn fathlǝnggighǝn ɗǝ ɗa nda wumang nafighǝn ɓa wurnǝn ahu ƙǝshiirha heu.”
\s1 Tsaharhaha aten ɗǝf shiɓaarha
\r (Matta24:32-35)
\p 
\v 28 “Walama tsaharhaha aten ɗǝf shiɓaarha. A naɗun ndǝn a tsǝtsǝtta, sǝnɗun sǝ nduwus fegrha ɓa.
\v 29 Ko nanǝn kee, a naɗun a naa ǝngginiya a katǝrarha hai, sǝnɗunsǝ nduwus ɗa ɓa tsau a mii kwatminda.
\v 30 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, nafiya ƙǝshiid weeriya mba nda a mǝra wa ƙǝl katǝrana ǝnggina hai ya.
\v 31 Nda talara tǝ hweeɗe na nda ngwalarha hai, amma laɓarna mbǝ tam ngwalarha wa.
\s1 Mbǝ niifa sǝ sǝngga farɗi nduwa sayidɗi wa
\r (Matta24:36-44; Luka17:26-30,34-36)
\p 
\v 32 “Mbǝ niifa sǝ na a sǝn farɗi nduwa sayidɗi na ǝnggini a katǝrarha hai ya wa, ko fathlǝngya na a talara, nduwa Wanɗi, ƙǝl chinɗi kee ndǝn sǝngga ndǝn.\f + \fr 13:32 \ft Matta 24:36 \f*
\v 33 Kwarama! A sǝnunsǝ sǝnggun ɓad sayidɗa ɓa wa.
\v 34 Nǝghǝn ƙǝla niifa na a wiirha, mal wurighǝnǝn ahar mafayighǝn, kowunni tǝ yighǝn taara fǝrang nǝn, ndanggǝn tǝ ƙǝla kwatkirma ha a shiiɗǝ wa.\f + \fr 13:34 \ft Luka 12:36-38\f*
\v 35 Tsaunǝn kee, a shiiɗun wa ƙǝsǝr sǝnggun farɗi na tǝ wuriɗi a ɓarha ɓa wa, tǝ a figrha, nduwa a manad fǝɗikrha, nduwa ka tǝtad ɗiyarha, nduwa a tsar.
\v 36 A ɓaɗa ɓa huhwam ɓa wa wal kun a shiirha wa.
\v 37 Ənɗi pǝrang ni kun ya, pǝranggi ndǝn kowunni kee, ‘A shiiɗun wa!’ ”
\c 14
\s1 Ƙǝnang mamngya Yahudaya hai a ɓǝlang ngganda Yeeso
\r (Matta26:1-5; Luka22:1-2; Yahaya11:45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Takhƙǝn ɓeena sǝri a ǝna wutsǝfayidɗa nda yi mburodi kula mekhna, mamnda firistaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha kanda a kaɗa kwaman ƙǝsang nda Yeeso ɓǝɓee ka a ɓǝlangganda.
\v 2 Amma ndaa nda, “Mbǝ a far wutsǝfayidɗiya wa, naɗǝ fiya har ƙǝm yanda.”
\s1 Ƙǝmang nda fǝɗeerha Yeeso teena a Mbetani
\r (Matta26:6-13; Yahaya12:1-8)
\p 
\v 3 Nana Yeeso a Mbetani a hǝb ǝnnarhami a minda ki niifa na nda aarha Siman na tǝ wanhad termeerha fa, kyagha nuneefa ɓa tǝ ƙǝthlikrha urdi na tǝ wuɗǝɓǝla fa kaan, mbalanggǝn mii ƙǝthlikrǝɗaɗǝ iranggǝn fǝɗedɗi aten Yeeso hai.\f + \fr 14:3 \ft Luka 7:37-38\f*
\p 
\v 4 Fingya nanda a hǝb ǝnnarhami a mbǝrha tal tǝ Yeeso sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ ndaa nda, “Kama sǝɓang nǝn fǝɗedɗa ɗǝ na ngga kee ya?
\v 5 Andam heng ɗaɗǝ nǝn kal wuɗǝɓǝl rapathlaarha yi hurarha tal, fǝrang nggǝnǝn fa yamiiya.” Tǝrgha yanangganda kaan.
\p 
\v 6 Amma ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Malaman lee, kama nun a ɓillaghǝn ka ǝnanǝn ˈya na ngga a nggi?
\v 7 Na fa yamiya sǝ hangga ahur nun, kala faara nggǝmna hur nun fǝraman kanda. Amma mbǝ kakwanni nun naarha na nggi wa.\f + \fr 14:7 \ft Nggǝr Ngwa Kumaarha 15:11 \f*
\v 8 Ənaɗǝ ˈya nǝn a mbang nda. ˈWa nǝn iree fǝɗedɗa fa ya ka yi panna.
\v 9 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, kalla mbǝrha pǝr nda laɓar Faara saaɗǝ ahu ƙǝshidɗiya, ˈya ǝnanǝn na nda a pǝrghǝn ɗǝ ƙǝm, ka a ɗalghǝnda teena.”
\s1 Nggǝm Yahuda fa a fǝr Yeeso nǝn
\r (Matta26:14-16; Luka22:3-6)
\p 
\v 10 Tǝrgha Yahuda Iskaryoti tal ahur kumkap sǝri ɗi, ɗǝgha thlǝmad mamnda firistaya ɗǝ ka a fǝr Yeeso nǝn a kanda.
\v 11 Tǝkka mamnda firistayini mbǝnda fa sǝk nǝn ˈya ɓangga ɓa nggǝma nda fa a fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝla nda. Ƙǝla sayi nǝn fa tǝ mbǝrha nǝn a fǝrang Yeeso kanda.
\s1 Hǝb Yeeso ǝnnadmid wutsǝfayid tǝɗaarha ɗǝ heu tǝ fatsahayighǝn
\r (Matta26:17-25; Luka22:7-14,21-23; Yahaya13:21-30)
\p 
\v 12 A katǝra far Wutsǝfayidɗi yi Mburodi kula Mekhna, farɗani na nda ǝna sataka tǝ wan kamnda yi Tǝɗaarha. Tsahangga fatsahayighǝn mee, “A yanggi na midwa ɗan nggorha fa ɗǝna hǝb ǝnnadmid wutsǝfayid tǝɗaarha sǝ?”
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrgha thlǝngga Yeeso sǝri ahur fatsahayighǝn ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗaama hur wupǝri ɗǝ, ɓana niifa wal kun tsǝb tǝ tsuliina ha, mbuwa ma samadghǝn.”
\v 14 Ndaman tǝ wuriɗi kyanǝn sa hai, “Tǝmalǝmnda ni tsakhka mee, ‘Na ƙǝn rongya a yanggi, niya hǝb ǝnnadmid Tǝɗaarha sǝ tǝ fatsahayina?’
\v 15 Nǝn a kyaɗang ƙǝnna kun na manggǝn, na tǝ mbǝd tsaukya sǝ hangga. Ngwaman ƙǝm fa a mbǝɗi.”
\p 
\v 16 Wiigha fatsahayini a wupǝri ɗaɗǝ, ɗa nda walghǝn ƙǝla thlǝghang na Yeeso kanda. Ngwa nda fa tǝ ǝnnadmid tǝɗadɗi a mbǝɗi.
\p 
\v 17 Tsǝna figrha hai, sǝlgha Yeeso ɓa tǝ kumkap sǝri ɗi.
\v 18 Tsauna nda hai kanda a hǝb ǝnnarhami, ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, tal ahur nun nǝn a fǝr nggi, yanɗi nani a hǝbrha tǝghǝn.”
\v 19 Kanda heu sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ na nda a ndang nda tǝtal tǝtal, “Mbǝ nggini wa, nduwa nggini wa?”
\p 
\v 20 Ndanggǝn kanda, “A hur nun ni kun na kumkap sǝriɗi ya, yanɗi na harnan tal hu ɗengnda.
\v 21 Na Wan Niifa a wiirha ƙǝla chireethleng nanda hai atenggǝn. Amma ǝn kawa ni a niifɗi fǝrgha ndǝn! A fadghǝn a nggushi nggǝt wa na ndan.”
\s1 Hǝb ǝnnadmid Chinǝm
\r (Matta26:26-30; Luka22:14-23; 1 Korontiyaya11:23-25)
\p 
\v 22 Na nanda a hǝb ǝnnarhami, tǝrangga Yeeso mburodi sǝ hwan parkad Faara nǝn atenggǝn, kyanggǝn hai fǝranggǝnǝn fatsahayighǝn ɗǝ, ndǝghǝn, “Thlamadghǝn; thlu fanna niya.”
\p 
\v 23 Tǝranggǝn wuhuleu aam inabi sǝ usa Faara nǝn, fǝranggǝnǝn kanda ɗǝ, sangganda.
\v 24 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Farna niya irang nanda ɗǝ ka fiya hang. Fara lǝɗangga ɗǝfmi Faara.\f + \fr 14:24 \ft Kyarhaɓa 24:8; Irmiya 31:31-34\f*
\v 25 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, mbiya nggǝr sa aam inabi ɓalwa, ƙǝl ahu kutǝryid Faara ndǝn ɓani sa weerindǝghǝn.”
\p 
\v 26 Ngwala nanda aah amshe, kya nda sǝ ɗǝnda wumnda ɗǝfya Dzaitun sǝ.
\s1 Na Mbiturus a ngaal sǝnda Yeeso
\r (Matta26:31-35; Luka22:31-34; Yahaya13:36-38)
\p 
\v 27 Ndangga Yeeso fatsahayighǝn, “Kun heu nun a kar nggi fa, ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn chichireethlee hai tǝ ndaarha;
\q1 “ ‘Niya ɗǝk tǝ lafadɗi,
\q2 na chaukhrayini a weela hai.’\x * \xo 14:27 \xt Dzakariya13:7\x*
\b
\m 
\v 28 Amma a kwasamadɗi thliini sǝ hu mǝrra, niya ˈwaarha Nggalili ɗǝ ma kun.”\f + \fr 14:28 \ft Matta 28:16\f*
\p 
\v 29 Ndaagha Mbiturus, “Ka kar nanda sa fa heu, nggi kam mbi naarha wa.”
\p 
\v 30 Ndangga Yeeso, “Mbiturus, niya puro ƙǝkafek, a fǝɗik weeriya kapa na kilngaara tǝtaarha sǝri, na ngaal sǝndǝna katǝra mahan.”
\p 
\v 31 Amma Mbiturus ɗǝgha mbeeɗǝ tǝ ndaarha, “Ko nǝm a mǝra ƙǝm kyab, mbi tam ngaal sǝnduwa wa.”
\p Fingya fatsahaya heu ndaa nda kee ƙǝm.
\s1 Hwan Yeeso Faara a Nggetsǝmani
\r (Matta26:36-46; Luka22:39-46)
\p 
\v 32 Ɗǝnda mbǝrha ɗǝ na nda aarha Nggetsǝmani, ndangga Yeeso fatsahayighǝn, “Tsawama a mbǝɗiya ɗǝni ka hwan Faara ɗǝ.”
\v 33 Tǝranggǝn Mbiturus, tǝ Yakubu tǝ Yahaya nagha tǝ ɓillaarha tǝ sǝbrha hura kaan.
\v 34 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Sǝb hurna ɗǝ ƙǝla ni mǝra. Tsawama a mbǝɗiya a shiiɗun wa.”
\p 
\v 35 Nduwusgha mbeeɗǝ, ɓǝrgha hweeɗa hai hwan faara a naɗǝ a ǝnaarha hai a ndǝkka hai tǝ sǝsadɗiya.
\v 36 Ndagha, “Pǝpa, ǝngya heu nǝghǝn pǝppa a fadwa. A nggǝmna fa tǝree sǝsadɗaɗǝ ya. Mbǝ nggǝmnda hurna wa, amma ˈya nggǝmna hurwa ndǝna mǝmǝl.”
\p 
\v 37 Tǝrgha wudgha thlǝmad fatsahayighǝn ɓa, ɓagha wal kanda a shiirha. Ndanggǝn Mbiturus, “Mbiturus, nun a shiirha? Mbun mbang tsaurha tsǝɓaku a ƙǝlaarha wa?
\v 38 A shiiɗun wa, hwanama Faara amanun mukrha hu ƙǝƙǝrra hai. Minnun sǝ ǝnaarha, amma thlu fannun mǝrɗa hai.”
\p 
\v 39 Tǝrgha Yeeso mal kanda ɗǝgha ka hwan Faara ɗǝ, nggǝrghǝn thlǝkrha ƙǝla ˈwanǝn hwanda.
\v 40 Nggǝrghǝn wutta thlǝmandan ɓa ɓagha wal kanda a shiirha faɗǝn, ƙǝsǝr ngwalang ɓeena fandan. Sǝngwanda ǝnɗi na nda thlǝghang nda wa.
\p 
\v 41 Wud nǝn ɓa yi mahan, ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɓal wun a shiirha tǝ yibrha? Tsǝkɗǝ kee! Ɓad sayidɗa ɓa. Fǝr nda Wan Niifa ahar fa ɗimiya hai.
\v 42 Thleema sǝ! Taama wiim! Kulo tǝ fǝrrǝna ɓayi ya!”
\s1 Ƙǝsang nda Yeeso
\r (Matta26:47-56; Luka22:47-53; Yahaya18:3-12)
\p 
\v 43 Nana Yeeso aten ndikrha kee, ƙǝlagha hai ka Yahuda, tal na ahur fatsahayighǝn kumkap sǝri ɗi kyagha ɓa tǝ fiya hangga a samadghǝn ngwanda fa tǝ thlakh ƙǝlarya tǝ sǝsalya. Thlǝnna mamnda firistaya kanda, tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha tǝ shingya.
\v 44 ˈWad Yahuda teena saghang ɗa ndǝn kanda tǝ ndaarha, “Yanɗi ndang ni ˈya tǝ fǝbrha, niifɗa ni; ƙǝsaaman win tǝghǝn ƙǝlaghǝnun ha ngga.”
\p 
\v 45 Ɓana Yahuda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa aaghǝnǝn, “Mala!” Fǝɓanggǝn.
\v 46 Tǝrgha ƙǝsangganda Yeeso, ƙǝsghǝnda ha ngga.
\v 47 Amma niifa tal ƙǝɗanggǝn thlaukh ƙǝlarghǝn sǝ kyathlanggǝn thlǝmad mafad mamnda firistaya ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 48 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Tǝrwun nggi niifa ni na tǝmbǝng, nun ɓaarha ɓa tǝ thlaukh ƙǝlarya tǝ sǝsalya ka a ƙǝseewun wa?
\v 49 Ƙǝtsar nggi a thlǝmad nun, nggi a tsaharhaha a pǝpal Wuri Faara, ƙǝseewun wa. Amma katǝra nǝn hai kee ka a lǝghǝdgha ˈya ndaana ɗeleewar Faara.”\f + \fr 14:49 \ft Luka 19:47; 21:37\f*
\p 
\v 50 Tǝrgha fatsahayighǝn kowunni ƙǝl ɗaarha mal Yeeso nda.
\p 
\v 51 Na wundǝlarha sǝ tal ahur nafiya na a mbu samad Yeeso, mbǝ lukrha sǝ a fadghǝn wa ƙǝl kooto kee ndǝn kaunǝn fa. Ɓana nafini ka ƙǝsang Yeeso ɓa,
\v 52 muwanggǝn kootodɗa ɗǝ na a fadghǝn ɗaagha tawalth.
\s1 Ɗǝnda tǝ Yeeso a mbed mamngya
\r (Matta26:57-68; Luka22:54-55; Yahaya18:13-14; 19:24)
\p 
\v 53 Ɗǝnda tǝ Yeeso a minda ki mamnda firistaya ɗǝ, a mbǝɗani wumna fingya mamngya firistaya sǝ, tǝ shingya, tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha.
\v 54 Mbuwa Mbiturus samad ndan ɗǝ a samarha inggun ta pǝpal minda ki mamnda firistayina ɗǝ. Tsauka hai a thlǝma fa ƙǝlaya ha nagha a tǝk waarha fa.
\v 55 Mamnda firistayini tǝ fingya wumngga hai na nda a kaɗa kwamana na a ƙǝsangganda Yeeso tǝ ˈya na ɗimi, tǝna nda ɓǝlang nda, amma wal wanda wa.
\v 56 Nggaɓangga fingya fa tǝ pathya hangga, amma ɓawa mii ndan ɓa tal wa.
\p 
\v 57 Tǝrgha thliigha fingya sǝ pǝr laɓarya nda yi nggaɓaarha ndaa nda,
\v 58 “Sǝk ɗan fadghǝn ndǝghǝn, ‘Niya chang Ƙǝn Faara hai tǝnna fiya, tǝngga pak ahu ɓeena mahan, mbǝ niifa ni a tǝnggǝn wa.’ ”\f + \fr 14:58 \ft Yahaya 2:19\f*
\v 59 Ko nanǝn kee tǝrwa path ndan kwamana wa.
\p 
\v 60 Tǝrgha mamnda firistayini thliigha sǝ a mbed fiya tsahang mee nǝn Yeeso, “Mba mbang nggǝra sǝ wa? Ma na ndaarha aten pathɗi thlǝkna nafini aten wa ya?”
\p 
\v 61 Amma nggasgha Yeeso tip, nggǝrwa sǝ wa.
\p Nggǝrgha mamnda firisyini tsahang mee, “Nduwa sani Ƙǝrǝsti, Wan Faara amshi tǝ Parka?”
\p 
\v 62 Ndangga Yeeso, “Nggini.
\b
\q1 Nun a naa Wan Niifa tsau a yisǝmad Faara Amshi na tǝ mamnggirha ha heu,
\q2 nǝghǝn ɓayi ahu hashmbe a talara hai.”\f + \fr 14:62 \ft Ndaniyel 7:13\f*
\b
\p 
\v 63 Tǝrgha mamnda firistayini djaranggǝn luwudghǝn ɗǝ, ndǝghǝn, “Palth ma nǝm nggǝr kaɗaarha faɗǝn?
\v 64 Sǝkɗǝm ndǝn hai a miighǝn laɓar sar Faara nda nǝn. Ma ndanun?”
\p Kanda heu ndaa nda, a ɓǝlangganda.
\v 65 Tǝrgha fingya katǝrang ngganda chahang yakhrha Yeeso fa; ƙǝnangganda yidghǝn mbighǝnda, ndang ngganda, “Kulo! Wun mbiigha sa hu sayidɗi ya, annabi?” Fa ƙǝla ƙǝn Faara ha ɗǝnda mbeeɗǝ tǝ ɗǝkƙǝn.
\s1 Ngaal Mbiturus sǝnda Yeeso
\r (Matta26:69-75; Luka22:56-62; Yahaya18:15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 66 Nana Mbiturus a pǝpal mindǝɗi a tǝk waarha fa, kyagha wee nuwun ɓa tal ahur mafaya mamnda firistayini.
\v 67 Nanǝn Mbiturus a tǝk waarha fa ƙǝlanggǝn ɗǝ ngga. Ndanggǝn, “Sa na tal ahur nafini na a mbu samad Yeeso tǝ Nadzarat ɗi.”
\p 
\v 68 Amma ngaalghǝnǝn. Ndanggǝn, “Sǝngwi ǝnɗi na a thlǝkrha ya wa,” thliigha sǝ ɗǝgha kwatkirma ɗǝ. Tǝrgha tǝtaagha ɗiyarha.
\p 
\v 69 Nggǝrna mafadɗi naghǝn, ndanggǝn nafini na ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗi, “Niifɗiya nǝghǝn tal ahur ndan.”
\v 70 Nggǝrghǝn ngaalghǝn faɗǝn.
\p Tsǝna nda tsǝɓaku, nafini na ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗi ndang ngganda Mbiturus, “Sa mbǝ ngaala sǝ wa na tal ahur ndan, ƙǝsǝr tǝ Nggalilad ni sa.”
\p 
\v 71 Katǝranggǝn ang shiurha tenggǝn fa ɓa ndǝghǝn, “Aahɗi Faara, sǝngwi niifɗi nun a thlǝkrha ya wa.”
\p 
\v 72 Tǝrgha tǝtaagha ɗiyarha yi sǝri. Ɗalgha Mbiturus teena hai tǝ laɓar Yeeso ndang nǝn, “Kapa na kidngaara tǝtaarha yi sǝri na ngaal sǝndǝna katǝra mahan.” Kwanggǝn tenggǝn hai nagha a tǝrha.
\c 15
\s1 Ɗǝnda tǝ Yeeso a mbed Mbilatus ɗǝ
\r (Matta27:1-2,11-14; Luka23:1-5; Yahaya18:28-38)
\p 
\v 1 A tsar ƙǝrǝt wumngga mamngya firistaya hai tǝ shingya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha, tǝ fingya kognaya ƙǝnangganda path ndan hai. Ƙǝnangganda Yeeso ɗǝnda tǝghǝn a mbed Mbilatus ɗǝ.
\v 2 Tsahangga Mbilatus mee, “Sani kutǝr Yahudaya wa?”
\p Nggǝmangga Yeeso, “Ƙǝla thlǝkna na.”
\p 
\v 3 Tǝrgha mamnda firisɗi nagha a ɗahang pathya fa aten ǝngya hangga.
\v 4 Nggǝrgha Mbilatus tsahang mee, “Mba nggǝra sǝ ndeye wa? Sǝkkwa ǝnɗi nana nda a thlǝworha fa wa!”
\p 
\v 5 Amma Yeeso kalwa sǝ wa, fǝrang ǝnwulteena nǝn Mbilatus.
\s1 Ngwang nda kumad mǝrra Yeeso
\r (Matta27:15-26; Luka23:13-25; Yahaya18:39—19:16)
\p 
\v 6 Kala wutsǝfayid tǝɗaarha yakh Mbilatus kal niifa hai tal muwang nanda hu porsǝna ɗǝ yi hwanna fiya.
\v 7 Na niifa sǝ thlǝmnggǝnni Mbarabas muwang nanda hu porsǝna ɗǝ ka tǝmbǝnggidghǝn ˈwanǝn ɓǝl niifa.
\v 8 Wumna fiya thlǝmad Mbilatus ɓa, hwanggǝnda a kalang niifa nǝn kanda hai na hu porsǝna ƙǝla nǝn tǝ ǝnaarha.
\v 9 Nggǝmanggǝn kanda ndǝghǝn, “Na minnun sǝ a kalang kutǝr Yahudaya ni kun hai wa?”
\v 10 Ƙǝsǝr sǝnɗasǝ ka sǝrǝkkid mamnda firistaya ni ɓang nanda Yeeso ɓa.
\p 
\v 11 Amma Mamngya firistaya shighangganda fiya fa a kalgha Mbilatus Mbarabas hai a meghed Yeeso.
\v 12 Ndangga Mbilatus kanda, “Amma a kalangɗi Mbarabas kun hai, niya ǝnaarha ƙǝn tǝ niifɗi nun aarha kutǝr Yahudaya?”
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrangganda urad ndan sǝ, “Tawaman ɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 14 Ndangga Mbilatus kanda, “Kama nda, ɗimid ma ǝna nǝn?”
\p Amma tǝrangga fiya urad ndan sǝ kaan, “Tawaman ɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 15 Nanǝn na mid Mbilatus sǝ a tǝkka fiya mbǝnda fa, kalang Mbarabas nǝn kanda hai. Tǝrgha fǝr Yeeso nǝn a tsaɗaghǝn nda, a fǝranggǝnǝn sodja Romaya tawangganda ɗǝ.
\s1 Sodjaya wanda Yeeso
\r (Matta27:27-31; Yahaya19:2-3)
\p 
\v 16 Sodja yini ɗǝnda tǝ Yeeso a mbǝd tar ndan ɗǝ, aah fingya sodjaya nda ɓa.
\v 17 Kalang kaɓad kutǝryirha nda fa na yiɓa, faɗang ngganda ndaha na nzǝnzang panggǝn nda atenggǝn.
\v 18 Tǝrgha tǝrangganda urad ndan sǝ na nda a ndangˈya, “Alvari! Kutǝr Yahudaya!”
\v 19 Na nda a ɗǝkƙǝn tǝ sǝsaala a tenggǝn, tǝ ƙǝm na nda a chahang yakhrha fa. Ɓǝra nda hai tǝ waɗeeyi ndan wai na nda a fǝrang mamnggirha yi waa farha.
\p 
\v 20 Ngwalang na nda waaghǝn, ƙǝɗangganda kaɓad kutǝryidɗa hai na a fadghǝn kalang yighǝn nda. Tǝrgha ɗǝnda tǝghǝn ƙǝshaaɗǝ ƙǝsǝr a ɗaa nda tawang ɗǝ.
\s1 Tawang nda Yeeso ɗǝ
\r (Matta27:32-44; Luka23:26-43; Yahaya19:17-27)
\p 
\v 21 Na nanda a wiirha tǝ Yeeso ƙǝma nda tǝ niifa na nda aarha Siman tǝ Sayirarha chin nda Alizanda tǝ Rufus, ɓaghǝn ɓa a Sarin. Ngyaɓang tǝr kaɗid ɗa nda fa.\f + \fr 15:21 \ft Romaya 16:13\f*
\v 22 Ɓa nda tǝ Yeeso a mbǝrha ɓa na nda aarha Nggolggota ndǝna mbǝd ɓalhwar teena.
\v 23 Fǝrang aam inabi nda kukurɗa tǝ mur,\f + \fr 15:23 \fk Mur:\ft Ɗǝf saarha ni na thlahang hatta fad niifa ɗǝ\f* amma karɗǝ saarha fa.
\v 24 Tǝrgha tawangganda Yeeso ɗǝ ndǝghangganda karidghǝn hai a pathlang ndan, Əna chacha nda aten lukkighǝn tǝ kurmi na niifa a waala.\f + \fr 15:24 \ft Dzabura 22:19\f*
\v 25 Tawangganda ɗǝ tǝ tsar fa.
\v 26 A man tenggǝn chireethleng ngganda ǝnɗa hai ɗahang nanda fa, “KUTƏR YAHUDAYA.”
\v 27 Tawang ngganda fathlee kwamangya ɗǝ sǝri, tal a yikawadghǝn, tal ƙǝm a yisǝmadghǝn\f + \fr 15:27 \ft Ishaya53.12\f*. Fingya chirethya yi kaar na nda tǝ mbǝdghǝn 28 tǝ ndaagha: “Lǝghǝtta palthɗa ni tǝ ndaagha, ‘Saghang nda ahur fa ɗimiya hai.’ ”\f + \fr 15:27 \ft Ishaya 53:12\f*
\p 
\v 29 Fiya na a mbǝraɗǝ na nda a thlǝghang pathya fa yi sar farha na nda a tsangˈya tendan fa na nda a waaghǝn, “Sa ndaagha na fǝlang Ƙǝn Faara hai na manggǝn tǝnangga hu ɓeena mahan,\x * \xo 15:29 \xt Dzabura22:8; 109:25; Markus14:58; Yahaya2:19\x*
\v 30 Hǝrghang fadwa lee tǝraa na hai aten kaɗidɗiya!”
\p 
\v 31 Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm, mamngya firistaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha na nda a waaghǝn, “Hǝrghanggǝn fingya, amma mbǝ mbang hǝrghang fadghǝn wa!
\v 32 Ngwa na Ƙǝrǝsti ɗa nǝm kutǝr Isǝrela, tǝrgha hai a ten kaɗidɗi naghǝnǝm tǝnǝm fǝrang ƙǝkafek!” Ko fathlee kwamanggini tawang nanda kanda ɗǝ tǝghǝn na nda a thlǝghang pathya fa mbuwa mbǝnggǝn.
\s1 Mǝrra Yeeso
\r (Matta27:45-56; Luka23:44-49; Yahaya19:28-30)
\p 
\v 33 Na yan faara a sǝrǝkrha wula nggǝlanggǝn chehwedɗi heu ta figrha ɗǝ.
\v 34 Tǝrgha a fiyidɗi tǝrangga Yeeso Uradghǝn sǝ, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabaktani?” Ndaarha ni, “Faarna, Faarna, kama nda malna nggi?” \x * \xo 15:34 \xt Dzabura22:1\x*
\p 
\v 35 Fingya na ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗi sǝkkwa ndan ngga wa tamngganda ndaarha nǝghǝn a aah annabi Ilya.
\p 
\v 36 Tal ahur ndan ɗagha ɗǝ tǝtǝnanggǝn soso tǝ aam inabi na chichakh panggǝn hu sǝsaala fǝranggǝnǝn sǝ ka a saagha. Ndaagha niifa, “Malaman, tama ƙǝlaghǝnǝm ha tǝ ɗǝna Ilya tǝrang hai.”\f + \fr 15:36 \ft Dzabura 69:21\f*
\p 
\v 37 Tǝrgha nggǝrgha Yeeso tǝrang uradghǝn sǝ, a mǝrgha.
\p 
\v 38 Shishamarɗi na ahu Ƙǝn Faara na manggǝn djaragha hai sǝri a talara hai ta hweeɗe hai.\f + \fr 15:38 \ft Kyarhaɓa 26:31-33\f*
\p 
\v 39 Mamnda Sodja Romaya na ƙǝƙǝt a mbed Yeeso fa naɗǝ kwamanɗi mǝrnǝn ndǝghǝn, “Ƙǝkafek, Wan Faarani ya!”
\p 
\v 40 Na fingya nishya sǝ a mbǝɗi na ƙǝƙǝt inggun a ƙǝlang ˈya na a katǝrarha hai. A hur ndan na Mairamu Makdaliya sǝ, Mairamu man Yakubu tǝ fewunda tǝ Yisufu, tǝ Salomi.
\v 41 Ka a Nggalili ɓa takkwana nishyina ndǝn ɓa na nda a ɗang sǝ tǝ tarya, na fingya nishya sǝ hangga a samadghǝn ka Urshalima ɓa.\f + \fr 15:41 \ft Luka 8:2-3\f*
\s1 Pang nda Yeeso
\r (Matta27:57-61; Luka23:50-56; Yahaya19:38-42)
\p 
\v 42 Katǝragha ǝnɗa hai ya a far ɗemnda yi far yiɓǝd Yahudaya, nanǝn tsǝ figrha hai.
\v 43 Na ka niifasǝ thlǝmnggǝnni Yisufu tǝ Aramatiya, nǝghǝn ahur mamngya na ƙǝnang pathla hai, Nǝghǝn a ƙǝla kutǝryid Faara fa. Tǝrǝm ngwa wa, ɗǝgha thlǝmad Mbilatus ɗǝ hwan mǝrra Yeeso nǝn.
\v 44 Fǝrwa Mbilatus ƙǝkafek mǝr Yeeso wa, aah mamnda Sodja Romaya nǝn ɓa tsahang mee nǝn.
\v 45 Pǝrangga mamnda sodja ɗa ndǝn, ndangga Mbilatus Yisufu a ɗǝgha tǝrang mǝrɗi.
\p 
\v 46 Hiigha Yisufu kaɓad pa mǝrra ɓa pǝpet, tǝranggǝn fad Yeeso ahu kaɗidɗi, faɗanggǝn Yeeso tǝ kaɓadɗi ɗǝgha ɗǝ panggǝn ahu kwaarha raa nanda hu feera. Kwatǝranggǝn feera ɓa na manggǝn nggǝlanggǝn kwadɗa sǝ.
\p 
\v 47 Mairamu Magdaliya tǝ Mairamu man Yisǝfu na mbǝɗa nda pang nanda Yeeso sǝ.
\c 16
\s1 Thlid Yeeso sǝ hu mǝrra
\r (Matta28:1-8; Luka24:1-12; Yahaya20:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Kyana far yiɓǝd Yahudayina ɗǝ, Mairamu Magdaliya tǝ Mairamu man Yakubu tǝ Salomi hii urdi nda na mindan sǝ ɗa nda ƙǝmang fad Yeeso tǝghǝn.
\v 2 A tsar far katǝra thlǝtta ɓeena, yanfaara a kyarha ɓa ƙǝs kwamana nda aten kwadɗa ɗǝ
\v 3 tsahang mee nda ndan ha, “Wunni a kwatǝrang ferɗi ƙǝm ɗǝ na a mii kwadɗi?”
\v 4 Amma tǝrang nanda tendan sǝ ƙǝla nda hai ferɗi na manggǝn kwatǝrang nda ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 5 Kyana nda ahur kwadɗa hai ƙǝla nda hai wundǝlarha tǝ lukrha fa pǝpet tsaua man yisǝma, tǝr ma nda.
\p 
\v 6 Ndanggǝn kanda, “A fidɗun hai wa, nun a kaɗa Yeeso tǝ Nadzarat tawang nanda ɗǝ. Thliiɗa sǝ ɓalwa mbǝɗiya wa. Kǝlaman mbǝɗi hunang nanda sa hai ya.
\v 7 Amma ɗamaɗǝ ɗun pǝranggǝn fatsahayighǝn tǝ Mbiturus tǝ ndaarha, ‘Nǝn a ˈwaarha Nggalili ɗǝ ma kun. Ɗǝnun naghǝn a mbǝɗi ƙǝla pǝrang nǝn kun.’”\f + \fr 16:7 \ft Matta 26:32, Markus 14:28 \f*
\p 
\v 8 Thliigha nishyini tǝ ɗaarha aten kwadɗi nagha fad ndan a rǝprha fa ka hǝreenga. Kalang ngwanda niifa sǝ wa, ƙǝsǝr ƙǝs hǝreenga kanda.
\s1 Kyad Yeeso fadghǝn a Mairamu
\r (Matta28:9-10; Yahaya20:11-18)
\p 
\v 9 Thliina Yeeso sǝ ahu mǝrra a far katǝra thlǝtta ɓeena ˈwaghǝn kyad fadghǝn a Mairamu Magdaliya nuɗi kyang nǝn ǝnkaheeya sǝ mǝd a fadghǝn.
\v 10 Ɗǝgha ɗǝ pǝranggǝn nafini na nanda tǝghǝn kaar na nanda tǝ sǝbrha hura kanda a tǝrha.
\v 11 Amma sǝkna nda na Yeeso tǝ yibrha, na ɗa ndǝn, fǝr wanda ƙǝkafek wa.
\s1 Kyad Yeeso fadghǝn a fatsahayighǝn sǝri
\r (Luka24:13-35)
\p 
\v 12 Akwasamadghǝn kyakhrangga Yeeso fadghǝn hai kyad fadghǝnǝn a fatsahayighǝn sǝri na nanda a kwaman ɗǝrha mbǝrha ɗǝ.
\v 13 Wuɗa nda ɗa nda pǝranggǝn shayindan, amma fǝr wanda ƙǝkafek tǝ path ndan wa.
\s1 Fǝrang Yeeso taara fatsahayighǝn
\r (Matta28:16-20; Luka24:36-49; Yahaya20:19-23; Tar fathlǝngya1:6-8)
\p 
\v 14 Tsǝɓaku kyadgha Yeeso fadghǝn a kumkap tal ɗi a sayidɗi na nanda a hǝb ǝnnarhami. Tǝrgha yananggǝn kanda ƙǝsǝr ka yamid fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan tǝ kakrakkin tendan fǝrang ngwanda ƙǝkafek nafini nagha ndǝn a kwasamadɗi thliinǝn sǝ.
\p 
\v 15 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗaama hu ƙǝshiirha ɗǝ ɗun pǝr laɓarɗi na mbǝnggǝn ya a fiya heu.\f + \fr 16:15 \ft Tar Fathlǝngya 1:8\f*
\v 16 Kala niifa fǝrgha ƙǝkafek ǝnang mbaptisǝma nda, nǝn a hǝrǝkrha, amma niifa fǝrwa wa ƙǝkafek na nda a ngwang kumarha sǝ.
\v 17 Fingya fǝrgha ƙǝkafek na nda a wal sǝsǝmnda ǝna ǝnwuteengya hangga. Hu thlǝmna na nda a kyang ǝnkaheeya sǝ, tǝ ƙǝm na nda a ndikrha tǝ fingya miiya pak.
\v 18 Na nda a ƙǝsang huthlingya tǝ haryindan, ko saa nanda warkami mbǝ ǝnang ˈya kanda wa. Na nda ɗǝfang haara haaya teena, ƙǝna nda.”
\s1 Tǝrang nda Yeeso talara ɗǝ
\r (Luka24:50-53; Tar fathlǝngya1:9-11)
\p 
\v 19 A kwasamadɗi ngwalana Yeeso ndikrha tǝ kanda, tǝrang ngganda talara ɗǝ tsauka a yisǝmad Faara.\f + \fr 16:19 \ft Tar Fathlǝngya 1:9-11\f*
\v 20 Tǝrgha fatsahayighǝn ɗǝnda mbeeɗǝ tǝ pǝr laɓar Faara, Chinǝm nǝghǝn tǝ kanda ha nagha. Nǝn naarha kyaɗang ƙǝkafekkid laɓarghǝn kanda tǝ ǝnwuteengya nanda a ǝnaarha.
